HiSi Glass is a family owned business in Northern California with over 40 years of experience developing and blowing technical tight-tolerance functional glass. Our mission is to offer a more scientific approach to the smoking and vaporizing experience with the intention to reduce health risks associated with inhaling hot, dry smoke or vapor. Our unique percolator designs maximize cooling and moisture conditioning for the ultimate in smoke and vapor delivery. We design our tubes and bubblers not only for optimized cooling and moisture conditioning, but also easy draw and durability. Get HiSi and enjoy the smoothest and fullest inhalations possible.

Overview
Flushmount downstem with 10mm tubing and step tip 11 hole diffuser. Accomodates 14mm male bowls; ashcatchers and drop downs. 3.5 inches from bottom of joint to tip.

Sculpted with ergonomics to fit comfortably in your hand, the device feels both sturdy & sleek. Grab an extra battery to keep on going. Can be charged individually with or without the body of the AERIS via USB-C.

data.name: Bowl Buster
data.desc:
NOW YOU NO LONGER HAVE ASHES collecting on your garage floor each day, or the terrible feeling of trying to blow the ash out of a pipe only to have it blown back into your eyes causing major discomfort.

Finding a quality-made, easy-to-use ashtray with an ashtray with the spike is hard. So you settle for the next thing under a tree and deal with it until it fails. Which it will.

Cheap knockoffs don't last, break easily, and don't work well. When you try to de-bowel the pipe, the poker doesn't actually do anything! You're going to have to get another one soon. And another one after that.
BUT YOUR SEARCH FOR THE IDEAL ASHTRAY ENDS HERE!!

SANTA CRUZ ASHTRAY is what you need. It's made of natural hemp and won't bend or break like those plastic ones do when you poke them too hard with the poker tool. It "debowls" very well, it's deep and my roach clip fits perfectly on the edge of it.

ERGONOMICALLY-DESIGNED ashtray looks elegant and a built-in poker tool is great to clean out glass & metal bowls. No need to scratch the bowl to remove the gunk because it is purpose-built to make it easier to clean.

data.name: Dash+

Grenco Science is proud to introduce the next generation of portable dry herb vaporizers with the G Pen Dash+. Following in the footsteps of its predecessor, the massively popular G Pen Dash, the Dash+ sports a similarly compact profile with notable upgrades, including hybrid heating technology, precise temperature control, and a full-color LED display.

Equipped with an easy-to-use 3-button interface, a full-color LED display, and haptic feedback, the Dash+ makes it easy to customize and view session status real-time, all with intuitive alerts. data.name: Gravity Infuser
data.desc:
Stündenglass® is honored to introduce the Gravity Infuser, a sophisticated and elegantly designed 360° rotating glass infuser that generates kinetic motion activation via cascading water displacement, opposing airflow technology and the natural force of gravity. Constructed using the highest quality materials, including borosilicate glass globes and aircraft-grade anodized aluminum, the Stündenglass Gravity Infuser elicits an immersive experience while delivering smooth, consistent and vaporous draws.

Designed for functional versatility, the Stündenglass Gravity Infuser is a complete set that includes an aluminum bowl kit and a glass liner, but can also connect to any smoking or vaporization device with a 14mm male joint. Using only fluid physics, a steady stream of smoke is force-air delivered through a 45° adjustable mouthpiece, providing an entirely contactless consumption.

A patented design backed by an extended 10-year warranty, the Stündenglass Gravity Infuser comes packaged in a reusable craft box with a handle, allowing for safe storage and transportation. Durable, futuristic in design and superb function, the Stündenglass Gravity Infuser stands alone at the pinnacle of smoking and vaporization devices.

data.name: Humidity Control 4
data.desc:
Boveda's patented 2-way humidity control continually responds to ambient conditions by adding or removing moisture to affect the enclosed environment and deliver the pre-determined relative humidity (RH) level printed on the pack.

It’s well known in science that certain salts mixed with water will naturally regulate humidity. We just patented the way that made it practical for packaging. Other packaging inserts either add moisture or remove moisture. Boveda does both, monitoring the RH (relative humidity) inside the container and regulating to the specific RH engineered into the Boveda.

Available in multiple sizes and humidity levels, Boveda can solve your intermediate moisture need and maintain the ideal moisture content of the items inside your container. Boveda uses all FDA-compliant ingredients and won’t damage anything through direct contact. The life of any Boveda depends how much moisture it releases, which will vary based on climate and container. You’ll know it’s time to replace Boveda when it’s no longer pliable.

It’s impossible for Boveda to over-humidify beyond the RH on the pack. That’s why their usage instructions talk about minimums, not maximums. There’s no such thing as using “too much”. More than the minimum will just last longer.

Use Case
Terpene retention and prevention of moisture loss.

How to Use
Boveda doesn’t need to be activated or maintained. Once the Boveda pack becomes rigid, it’s out of water and needs to be replaced. This could mean weeks to years, depending on the package or container, how much the container is opened/closed and the ambient environment. Yeah, it’s really that simple. For medical instruments, we also know that a number of Boveda formulas are stable under gamma radiation sterilization.

Size
Size 4: Supports up to 1/2 oz. (14 grams) of cannabis

products.name: Toro Vaporizer Heating Coil Part
products.desc: The heating coil has a ceramic housing and a coil that enables even heating and quicker cooldown times. To replace a burnt-out coil, wait until the old one is cooled down, unscrew it from the Toro E-rig base, and screw in the replacement heating coil. It is recommended to wipe down the whole device after every use with an alcohol wipe to keep the parts working properly.

The CartDub wears two hats - it not only preheats cartridges but also serves as an adept oil recovery system, ideal for personal use.

CARTDUB COMPLETE KIT INCLUDES:
- 18 Gauge Aluminum Tray for Oil Recovery
- CartDub Plate with 510 Thread port used to unlock "locked" prefilled oil cartridge tops, and 10 ports for cartridges for easy oil removal or cartridge pre-heat and fill
- Dab Concentrates Scalpel
- Dab Tools (shovel + spatula)
- 2 x 3ml Syringes
- 4 x Assorted Blunt Tip Needles
- PG/VG Oil Recovery Solution
- Proprietary Removal Pliers for locked prefilled cartridge tops
- Long Lever Wedge Bar used to open locked tops in 1.0 ml prefilled cartridges (tall)
- Short Lever Wedge Bar used to open locked tops in 0.5ml prefilled cartridges (standard)

data.name: CartDub Oil Removal Tool Set
data.desc:
It's not working and there is still oil in the tank, what should you do? The 510 thread tank fails, how do you recover the oil?
Fixing a broken cart: what are the steps involved? Even if your vape pen doesn't work, there are still ways to get your oil back. What happens if the battery in your disposable pen dies before you've used up the ink? What's the best way to go from one oil tank to the next? How do you avoid having to clean up a messy pen refill? With the HoneyStick Oil Recovery Kit, you'll have all the answers to your questions about broken vape tanks, dead vape cartridges, and non-working vape pens thanks to this low-cost little kit that includes everything you need to salvage your precious oil.

Oil Removal Kit Includes:

2 x Filling Syringes
4 Blunt Tip Needles
2 Syringe Caps
1 PG/VG 3ml Mixer Liquid

You can safely salvage/extrapolate oils by using the contents and watching our instructional video. You can use the blunt needle tips included in each kit to extract thick or thin oils from broken vape cartridges or navigate into a cartridge that no longer works and has a small space between the center post. Each kit includes different length and gauge (thickness) blunt needle tips. As a seasoned vaper, you know that having a flat tire is something that will happen to you at some point while driving. This kit will help you avoid losing your expensive oils when that happens. Bring order to your life with this handy little set!

data.name: 510 Cartridge
data.desc: 100% cannabis-derived and strain-specific, sourced from Maven’s premium indoor flower. Blended in curated ratios with our ultra-refined potent cannabis oil and cannabis-derived terpenes, our award-winning Gold Blends create an exceptional Entourage Effect, amplifying the best qualities of Maven’s signature strains.

products.name: 98 Reserve
products.desc: 98 Reserve, a tribute to our progress. This innovative Indica cross captures the timeless essence of Pre 98 Bubba Kush, elevated with the modern classic Runtz. These sugar-coated buds emit a musky, herbal aroma with pungent notes of conifer and citrus that tingle the nostrils, followed by sweet, woodsy undertones that culminate in a robust, coffee-like exhalation.

products.name: Key Lime Jack
products.desc: Key Lime Jack is an effervescent Sativa with a bright and summery aroma. This cross of Bling Cheesecake and Jack Herrer has sweet, sharp, and slightly sour citrus notes that fill the air upon opening a jar, creating a zesty and refreshing inhale. A skunky and earthy exhale instantly uplifts the mind, relaxes the body, and boosts your mood. This cerebral buzz is bubbly, long-lasting, and offers a euphoric high while increasing focus and keeping the mind sharp and alert.

products.name: Orange Belini
products.desc: Orange Bellini, a delightful cross of two of our most beloved strains, Orange Truffle Soufflé and Peach Crème Gelato, is a sweet, uplifting treat perfect for elevating any daytime experience. This sticky, resinous flower is deep in color, with contrasting violet foliage and orange stigmas beneath a dense layer of glistening trichomes. These sweet, citrus-forward nugs have an effervescent aroma reminiscent of fresh orange peels, grapefruit, and pine, with a flavor profile just as enticing. Orange Bellini sends the mind soaring higher with every fruity inhale and earthy exhale. Like its parent strain Orange Truffle Soufflé, an energizing head buzz increased focus, and creative stimulation is at the forefront of this high, with physically relaxing and anti-inflammatory properties from Peach Crème Gelato offering a well-rounded and balanced high.

products.name: RS-X
products.desc: RS-X is a testament to its remarkable lineage, featuring our potent Black Diamond X and RS11, bred by Deo Farms. Although the bud structure is dense, this frosty variegated flower features a permeating fragrance of mixed fruit that intensifies when ground. Each inhale reveals a swirl of rich, complex undertones, blending earthy diesel with sour citrus, leaving a satisfying tang on the tip of the tongue. This Indica dominant strain melts away discomfort and dissolves worries, leaving users in a colorful state of euphoria.

products.name: Shangri LA
products.desc: Behold the timeless Shangri-la. This harmonious fusion of Opal and Paradiso #11 displays mountainous buds in captivating tones of lush forest green and royal violet, set against a backdrop of pure white snow that blankets their majestic peaks, resembling a scene of a mystical utopia. Revel in a sensory voyage of unrivaled bliss with a blend of delicate floral aromas and luscious fruit enhanced by whispers of earthiness and diesel while a symphony of tart, candied notes linger on the palate. This enchanting Indica-dominant Hybrid is a treasure of a strain that rivals heaven on earth for those seeking peace and tranquility.

products.name: Silver Iris OG
products.desc: Silver Iris OG is an exceptional Indica-dominant Hybrid that embodies the regal lineage of our Maven OG and Zkittlez, with elegant sage green buds and prominent amber hairs that contrast a fine, pearly coating of trichomes. The rich fragrance of timeless, earthy OG mingles with hints of floral citrus that blossom into a lively arrangement when exhaled, leaving a delicate essence of fruit on the tongue. Like a flower that thrives under tender care, this strain cultivates a deep sense of mindfulness and contentment, grounding one in body, mind, and soul.

products.name: Sour Sangria
products.desc: Sour Sangria is an award-winning Sativa with a sophisticated flavor profile and well-balanced high. This compelling cross of our own Yuzu Mac and Pandora makes for dense, resinous nugs that display vivid blue and Fuschia tones. Its sweet, sour, and citrus-forward nose translates to a refreshing inhale, while floral, earthy, and peppery notes make for a bold exhalation. While this high can have calming and reflective qualities, its uplifting nature keeps the mind sharp, focused, and engaged.

These cartridges are crafted from fresh frozen premium flower and are certified by a state-certified independent laboratory. Humble Root offers quality cannabis to get you feeling just right under the influence of good vibes.

products.desc:
Kurvana’s Astro Queen cannabis vape cartridge contains high-quality cannabis oil extracted from the whole plant. Astro Queen is a unique and exciting hybrid strain that was made by crossing the Astro Boy strain with the alluring Space Queen strain. The result is an indica-dominant hybrid that will take you to new cosmic heights! 

Astro Queen’s THC level is a potent 91.38% with a low CBD level of 0.22%. Unlike some THC cartridges on the market, Kurvana’s Astro Queen cartridge, like all of our cartridges, are made using the entire plant, so the THC content is native to the individual strain. Likewise, the aroma and flavor profile of the strain is fully expressed in the finished product. Savor Astro Queen’s naturally rich, berry-forward flavor and aroma in the convenience of a cartridge.

data.desc:
Big Chief is a name recognized by those who run the game, not those who follow it.

After years working from the bottom to the top, Big Chief was built on a reputation for uncompromised quality amongst imitators.

Overview
Big Chief cartridges contain distilled cannabis oil and food-grade terpenes derived from the organic plants. There is no use of any sort of cutting agents, such as Vitamin E acetate, Emulsifier, or other synthetic products that can possibly alter the cannabis oil and terpene formulation.

All products are lab tested. Big Chief extracts are famous for being pure cannabis oil distillates.

data.name: Carbon Cart
data.desc: CARBON21 is our pinnacle vape line, consisting of carefully curated raw concentrates in our latest hardware. We pair our proprietary live-plant curation with a unique extraction method for each strain in this line. Deliberately crafted in small batches, each strain is presented in its rawest concentrate form—rich with the cannabinoid, flavonoid and terpene complexities of the live cannabis plant.

products.name: Black Jack Diamonds
products.desc: Blackjack Diamonds is a blissful, indica-dominant hybrid cannabis strain. Users enjoy Blackjack Diamonds for its euphoric properties, which create a clear-headed mindset that helps many users find focus and clarity. Blackjack Diamond is a cross of Black Domina and Jack Herer – two earthy strains with spicy undertones.

products.name: Chocolope Sauce
products.desc:
Indulge in the sweet, rich chocolate flavor of Chocolope Sauce and elevate your cannabis experience. This decadent sativa is a High Times Cannabis Cup winner for its remarkable flavor and aromatics that are reminiscent of raw cacao beans, as well as for its unparalleled effects. You’ll savor not only cacao, but also notes of sweet juicy melon, in this top shelf THC vape cartridge. 

Chocolope Sauce was made by crossing the strains Chocoolate Thai and Cannalope Haze. A classic combination, this sativa can trace its roots back to the 1980s, long before cannabis had taken off in the United States. 

Chocolope Sauce comes in a pre-filled cartridge and is compatible with most standard 510 thread batteries, making it easy to use and portable. Also available as an All-In-One option.

products.name: Lemon Cherry Gelato Diamonds
products.desc:
Lemon Cherry Gelato Diamonds is part of our CARBON21 line of concentrates. Crafted in small batches, this strain is presented in its raw concentrate form, with all of the cannabinoid, flavonoid, and terpene complexities of the live plant. 

Savor the sweet flavors of ripe cherry, lemon and earth in this deliciously potent indica. Made by crossing the Sunset Sherbet strain with the G.S. Cookies strain, Lemon Cherry Gelato boasts a richly flavorful terpene profile. Its fruit-forward flavors become more pronounced in concentrate form, without ever becoming overwhelming. Concentrate enthusiasts will appreciate the crystalline structures, or the “diamonds” that are naturally present in this terpene-rich sauce.

products.name: Lemon Royal Sauce
products.desc:
Lemon Tree x GMO
As bold lemon notes burst through a grassy euphoria, stimulating effects will uplift your state of mind.

products.name: Mango Mojito Badder
products.desc:
Part of Kurvana’s CARBON21 line, Mango Mojito Badder sativa cartridge is a potent, terpene-rich concentrate that was crafted using the whole live cannabis plant. You’ll enjoy an elevated trip to the tropics as you inhale this vape’s bright mango, citrus and sweet flavor and aroma. 

Reminiscent of the cocktail for which this strain was named, Mango Mojito is full of tropical flavor that is best enjoyed at a slow, even pace. It boasts a smooth vaporizing experience that speaks of its lineage and terpene profile, and the aromatics are as luscious as the taste.

products.name: Miracle Cake Badder
products.desc: Miracle Cake Badder is one of the most decadent, yet refreshing concentrates you’ll savor.  Ice Cream Cake and MAC genetics give this indica-dominant hybrid its beautiful sweet floral and earthy aroma, with a delicious and crave-worthy flavor profile reminiscent of its name.

data.desc: Looking for top-quality cannabis products? Look no further than Alien Labs, the premier source for all your cannabis needs. Alien Labs is passionate about providing customers with the very best cannabis products available, and uses only the finest ingredients and cutting-edge technology to ensure that you get the most out of every puff.Alien Labs is one of the first California cannabis brands that decided to start taking risks and showing up in the new California market when the majority wanted to stay hidden in the shadows. Since it's genesis of taking well known flower strains and making them seem almost otherworldly, to now pushing the “exotic” conversation forward by creating new and unique exotic strains. Alien Labs is for the connoisseur who has tried everything, knows what quality is, and wants to experience new strains.

data.name: CUREpen Cart
data.desc: West Coast Cure brings years of connoisseur cannabis mastery to the table, effortlessly offering consumers the best marijuana experience. With an award-winning pedigree and that extra something special, West Coast Cure is the go-to cannabis label for the true connoisseur. It’s not something West Coast Cure works at; they simply have a Passion for Cannabis.

products.name: Banana Smoothie
products.desc:
West Coast Cure CUREpen Cart (1g) - Banana Smoothie
Experience the rush of a great Banana Smoothie! A perfect vape when you need to stimulate your day, the Banana Smoothie 510 CUREpen Cartridge expresses flavors of creamy bananas and gassy citrus. A tropical Hybrid vape with chill effects, the Banana Smoothie cartridge provides serene results with a motivational kicker.

products.name: Birthday Cake
products.desc:
West Coast Cure CUREpen Cart (1g) - Birthday Cake
West Coast Cure’s Birthday Cake CUREpen Cartridge offers both mental respite and toothsome flavor. An Indica-dominant Hybrid oil, the Birthday Cake 510 Cartridge produces a creamy vanilla flavor with nutty undertones. A relaxing way to end your day on a high note, this full gram cartridge makes any special day just a tad bit sweeter.

products.name: Biscotti
products.desc:
West Coast Cure CUREpen Cart (1g) - Biscotti
The Biscotti CUREpen Cartridge by West Coast Cure is a 1-gram tank of Indica-dominant oil. Loaded with oil from the namesake strain’s sweet and spicy terpene profile – a cross of Gelato #25 and South Florida OG – this cart instills a tranquil mindset and establishes an atmosphere for critical thinking.

West Coast Cure CUREpen Cart (1g) - Grape Ape
The Grape Ape CUREpen Cartridge by West Coast Cure is an 50/50 Hybrid that can inspire a tranquil and joyous outlook for the average consumer. A genetic mashup between Mendocino Purps, Skunk, and an Afghani Landrace, the full gram Grape Ape 510 Cartridge is a grape-centric vape that delivers a perfect wind-down after a busy day of work.

products.name: Jack Herer
products.desc:
West Coast Cure CUREpen Cart (1g) - Jack Herer
The Jack Herer CUREpen Cartridge is based on the classic Jack Herer strain. A full gram Sativa-dominant vape, the oil in this 510 Cartridge creates the classic ‘Herer’ flavor with hints of lemon, pine, wood, and spice. A great motivator, this cartridge cultivates a sense of energetic bliss mixed with a dash of creative joy.

An intoxicating dessert for the head, the oil in this 510 Cartridge has a motivational nature that makes it a terrific mid-day vape that creates a happy and upbeat headspace.

A classic vape that blends two noteworthy strains, the White and Appalachia, this full gram 510 Cartridge instills a sense of creative euphoria. A great wake-and-bake vape, this 1 gram Cartridge kick-starts your day in a flavorful way.

data.desc: Alien Labs is one of the first California cannabis brands that decided to start taking risks and showing up in the new California market when the majority wanted to stay hidden in the shadows. Since it's genesis of taking well-known flower strains and making them seem almost otherworldly, to now pushing the “exotic” conversation forward by creating new and unique exotic strains. Alien Labs is for the Connoisseur who has tried everything, knows what quality is, and wants to experience new strains. The finer things, for those that like their finer things a little weird.

products.name: Agent X
products.desc:
Alien Labs Live Resin Cart (1g) - Agent X
Agent X combines Atomic Apple and Xeno #1 for a minty smell and taste. The perfectly balanced hybrid hits strong, with an uplifting head effect and a relaxed body vibe.

products.name: Area 41
products.desc:
Alien Labs Live Resin Cart (1g) - Area 41
Area 41 has a sweet smell with citrus and floral undertones, a smooth flowery smoke with trichomes that put out a sweet and earthy aroma. This strain will give you an immediate feeling of euphoria along with a relaxed yet motivated mental focus and this is best reserved for those looking for a new heavy hitter.

products.name: Atomic Apple
products.desc:
Alien Labs Live Resin Cart (1g) - Atomic Apple
The live resin inside is of the highest possible quality, made from the fresh-frozen top-shelf flower that Alien Labs is known for. They created Krypto Chronic as a combination of Fruity Pebbles OG x Alien Cookies and Jet Fuel Gelato. It tastes and smells like you put gas in your bowl of fruity pebbles, with a fruity berry sweetness and pleasant creamy, gassy funk that will linger in the room.

data.name: Live Resin Cart
data.desc:
Our award-winning 100% Live Resin Cartridge embraces the natural expression of terpenes and cannabinoids in each strain. URSA cartridges are extracted from high quality, fresh-frozen cannabis sourced from premiere California cultivators.

We harvest and flash freeze the whole cannabis flower at its peak. Our extractors use cutting-edge technology to convert premium jared live resin to a dab on-the-go. URSA cartridges are manufactured with toxin-free dental grade ceramic. URSA Humboldt Live is 100% single origin live resin that provides a flavor experience “as the plant intended”. The rich combination of single strain terpenes and cannabinoids make this cart a consumer favorite.

products.name: Blueberry
products.desc: The sweet flavors of fresh blueberries combine with relaxing effects to produce a long-lasting sense of euphoria.

products.name: Forbidden Fruit
products.desc: Forbidden Fruit is the mouthwatering cross of Cherry Pie x Tangie. The indica effects hit hard between the eyes and lay into the body with each hit. Forbidden Fruit’s deep physical relaxation and mental stoniness make it perfect for dulling minor physical discomfort and discarding stress.

products.name: Lemon Head
products.desc:
Lemon Head is the delicious result of Lemonade being crossed with Lemon. Both awesome strains! This crossing created a sativa heavy beast that offers energising and cerebral highs.
The taste offered by Lemon Head is a mouth-watering mix of sweet and sour, with pungent tones of lemon punching through the centre of the mix.
This high is perfect for when pursuing creative projects, or when seeking enhanced focus and inspiration.

products.name: Passion Fruit
products.desc:
This potent sativa is a cross of Sweet Pink Grapefruit and Orange Bud, and it’s best known for its amazing smell and flavor. As you could have guessed from its lineage, Passion Fruit will give you a lot of sweet citrus and a nice floral note to balance it all out.

Passion Fruit provides an epic sense of euphoria and a desire to raid the pantry. Be sure to have snacks ready!

products.name: Pineapple Punch
products.desc: Pineapple Punch delivers a medley of pineapple, tropical citrus, and sweet floral flavors, while the uplifting, lighthearted effects provide a vacation from stress and bad moods.

data.name: Live Resin Cart
data.desc: Baked Bar Vape is considered one of the finest and purest THC carts, with multiples of juicy top flavors anyone can pick from. Like most vape cartridges’, baked bar THC vapes are both used for medical and recreational reasons. This vape is skillfully created with California’s finest cannabis strains. These carts are lab tested and pesticides free with THC levels of about 89.67% THC. Baked Bar carts are some of the best and purest carts in the markets today.

products.name: Afghan Gold
products.desc: Baked Bar Live Resin Cart (1g) - Afghan Gold Afghan Gold is an Indica-dominant hybrid strain with sharp aromas of pungent skunk and earthy hash. The flavor is light, with sweet florals and spicy herbs playing together perfectly on the tongue. The high is just as delightful as the flavor with full-bodied effects that will calm any mental or physical ache and pain as your mind lifts into a state of happiness and ease.

products.name: Candy Land
products.desc: Baked Bar Live Resin Cart (1g) - Candy Land Candy Land is a happy, Sativa-dominant strain with an upbeat, stimulating high that spurs creativity and provides energy for daytime tasks. Expect euphoria with a strong mood boost and some relaxation. It has a strong, sweet flavor and smell, with an earthy, spicy undertone.

products.name: Crystal Kush
products.desc: Baked Bar Live Resin Cart (1g) - Crystal Kush Crystal Kush has an earthy aroma with pungent and woody with notes of citrus and herbs. When consumed, its earthy flavor comes with a floral sweetness that complements its woodsy scent.

Expect a creativity spark as your mood gradually improves.

products.name: Northern Lights

products.name: Garlic Juice
products.desc: Garlic Juice is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between GMO and Papaya. Garlic Juice is 31% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Leafly customers tell us Garlic Juice effects include relaxed, happy, and sedated. Medical marijuana patients often choose Garlic Juice when dealing with symptoms associated with pain, sleep, and depression.

products.name: Grapes N Cream
products.desc: Grapes and Cream, also known as “Grapes ‘N Cream,” is a hybrid weed strain made by crossing Grape Pie with Cookies and Cream. This sweet combination results in a calming strain beloved by many cannabis connoisseurs. Smoking Grapes and Cream produces creative effects that stimulate your mind while leaving your body relaxed and prepped for sleep. This strain is ideal for late afternoon or evening hours and pairs best with projects that require creative thinking. Grapes and Cream features a grape flavor profile with surprising notes of pear and vanilla shining through. The dominant terpene of this strain is myrcene, followed by pinene. This original breeder of this strain is unknown. Strains similar to Grapes and Cream include Bruce Banner, Citrus Farmer, Carl Sagan, and T-1000.

products.name: Honey Guava
products.desc: A sativa-leaning hybrid from the Cookies Fam, Honey Guava is a Gelato phenotype. Noted for its fruity and gassy aroma and flavor, this strain is great for anyone with a sweet tooth. Honey Guava was selected and celebrated as a good strain to start the day with, so next time you have a busy Saturday, grab this strain to make it through.

products.name: Madd Fruit
products.desc: Madd Fruit is the mouthwatering cross of Cherry Pie x Tangie. This sumptuous genetic cross expresses a beautiful dense bud structure with deep purple hues, dark green foliage, and wiry orange hairs. The terpene profile is a perfect mixture of Cherry Pie’s musky, sweet cherry undertones and Tangie’s loud tropical flavors. There are also notes of pine, mango, and passionfruit candy. The indica effects hit hard between the eyes and lay into the body with each hit. Forbidden Fruit’s deep physical relaxation and mental stoniness make it perfect for dulling minor physical discomfort and discarding stress.

products.name: Papaya Bomb
products.desc: Papaya is an indica-dominant hybrid cannabis strain that is known for producing a mental calmness, though many consumers also find that this strain makes them energetic and productive. Nirvana Seeds bred this to be their take on a Mango strain and crossed Citral #13 with Ice #2 to make their own fruit. They met their own challenge and Papaya smells uncannily like its namesake. The taste is similar to its tropical fruit counterpart, but a spicy, peppery side also becomes apparent. The plants stay fairly short and thin, producing lots of fluffy buds with papaya-orange hairs in 8 or 9 weeks.

products.name: Pressure
products.desc: Pressure is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Gary Payton and Rainbow Chip. This strain is a frosty and colorful delight that produces a potent and balanced high. Pressure is 21% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Leafly customers tell us Pressure effects include feeling relaxed, happy, and giggly. Medical marijuana patients often choose Pressure when dealing with symptoms associated with anxiety, stress, and depression. Bred by LUVLI, Pressure features flavors like citrus, pepper, and orange. The dominant terpene of this strain is limonene.

products.name: Tractor Fuel
products.desc: Embark on an exploration of the Tractor Fuel strain, a potent hybrid born from the legendary Original Diesel BX1 and Skywalker OG BX1. This powerhouse strain captivates with its remarkable potency and complex aroma profile that promises an unforgettable experience for both recreational users and medical patients alike. A robust hybrid combining Original Diesel and Skywalker OG genetics.

products.name: Zerealz x HoneyDrop
products.desc: ereal is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Cereal Milk and Zkittlez. This strain is 50% sativa and 50% indica. Zereal is 20% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. We are still learning about Zereal’s effects, flavors, and medical uses. If you’ve smoked, dabbed, or consumed Zereal, please tell us about your experience by leaving a strain review.

data.name: Live Rosin Cart
data.desc:
Solventless, single-strain


Solventless live rosin will be increasingly popular as the public begins to experience the quality and freshness of these new vape carts.
Growing evidence suggests that cannabis which is grown from seed in the sun, in native soil such as we have in Humboldt County, produces the richest and most desirable flower for live rosin production.
The clean, smooth flavor of these solventless products capture the full-spectrum essence of the cannabis flower in a way that will excite old-school cannabis connoisseurs and new consumers alike.

data.name: Live Rosin Cart
data.desc:
Here at DabLogic our purpose is to cultivate the good life, which is why growing in living soil, hand trimming our buds & packaging our products in sustainable packaging is so important to us! We believe everyone should have access to the best cannabis and cannabis concentrates, so we won't compromise on our cultivation methods. It's not the easiest or least expensive way to grow great cannabis, but we believe it is the best.

Only the most pristine & exquisite flower from the Verde Natural garden are selected to be transformed into DabLogic handmade solventless hashish. This intense dedication to quality and belief in the healing power of plant medicine, produces a live resin that is unrivaled by the competition. By only using old school ice water hash techniques and pressing methods with low heat and pressure we make the best expressions of cannabis in hash form, with no fillers, cutting agents or toxic chemicals. Come experience our divine magical trichomes.

Half gram vape cartridge.

Overview
Dablogic solventless vape cartridge. Made from single sourced Verde Natural live soil flower. These cartridges have no fillers, additives, or cutting agents.

data.name: Live Rosin Solventless Cart
data.desc:
Solventless live rosin will be increasingly popular as the public begins to experience the quality and freshness of these new vape carts.

Growing evidence suggests that cannabis which is grown from seed in the sun, in native soil such as we have in Humboldt County, produces the richest and most desirable flower for live rosin production.

The clean, smooth flavor of these solventless products capture the full-spectrum essence of the cannabis flower in a way that will excite old-school cannabis connoisseurs and new consumers alike.

data.name: Mad Labs Cart
data.desc:
Mad Labs is mad for science. Everything from their hardware to their extraction methods is carefully engineered to give you the best end product.

1 full gram cartridge.

Overview
Mad Lab's proprietary formula has been perfected using hydrocarbon extraction. The process results in clean, terpene-rich, high-quality products that provide the full potential of the plant's medicinal value. Our licensed operations are built on a foundation of compassion, developed from the onset of California’s earliest medical cannabis regulations.

Their new, bigger tip, was designed to increase the air-flow while barely expanding the dimensions of the cartridge itself. The tip was completely re-engineered, reducing the borders by 40%, allowing for smoother hits and better flavor to elevate your vaping experience. Now that’s something to smile about.

data.name: Melted Diamonds Tank
data.desc:
Supherb is a lifestyle brand dedicated to revolutionizing the cannabis industry with a pioneering approach that combines state-of-the-art technology with a user-friendly airflow adjustment to provide a luxurious vaping experience. Our new technology allows us to create a pocket-sized, draw-activated vape pen while keeping the power necessary to produce a silky smooth vape cloud. All that power and a system that focuses on adjustable air filtration and not the heat source which eliminates overheating, potency issues, while preserving the flavor you desire. What does all that mean?

That means you can manually adjust the airflow setting anywhere between a quick sneaky toke or a hit that leaves you totally lifted. When you combine our battery, with our lab-tested, artisanal blended cannabis cartridges, you will experience a Supherb vaping experience. All products are tested by Encore Labs and accompanied by a holographic sticker so you can be sure that you are getting the Supherb quality you deserve.

Overview
Get high with Supherb’s melted diamonds cartridge packaged in their SUB-OHM vape tanks. Enjoy high potency THC in its purest form.

products.name: Blackberry Kush
products.desc:
Kurvana’s Blackberry Kush strain is an indica cross of the Afghani and Blackberry strains. A beauty to behold in its original flower form, Blackberry Kush is a colorful bouquet of violet, orange, yellow and dark green. When extracted as part of our Originals line, all of the gorgeous terpenes are preserved, allowing their full flavor and potent effects to shine through.

Rich, sweet dark berry and earth notes characterize this strain, along with a pleasant woodsy aroma that may trigger memories of picking berries in the fall. Blackberry Kush is slightly peppery thanks to the presence of beta caryophyllene, but it is also a smooth vape with long-lasting flavor and effects.

products.name: G.S. Cookies
products.desc:
G.S. Cookies strain hits the spot with a creamy, earth, chocolate cookie flavor and a rush of effects from full-spectrum cannabinoids. A hybrid vape that soothes the body and stimulates the mind, this will become your favorite cannabis oil cartridge from the first draw. This is a strain that has won many awards over the years, and for good reason: its effects and flavor profile are unmatched!
Part of our Originals line, G.S. Cookies has taken its place as one of the most highly sought-after hybrid THC vapes. This indica-dominant strain was originally made by crossing OG Kush with Durban Poison. The result is a flavorful and aromatic strain with notes of sweet mint, cookie, and earth. This one is perfect for an after-dinner treat.

products.name: Lemon Haze
products.desc:
Kurvana’s Lemon Haze sativa vape offers an uplifting aroma of fresh lemon peel and a burst of sweet, tangy fruit at the moment of inhalation. The strong citrus aromatics are due to the relatively high concentrations of limonene, its predominant terpene.

The powerful impact of this sativa strain is owed to the parent genetics of the Lemon Haze strain: Sativa Silver Haze and Lemon Skunk, both popular for their fast onset and energizing cerebral effects. As the offspring of this cross, Lemon Haze (sometimes written as Lemonhaze), carries the best of its parents’ characteristics.

The Lemon Haze cartridge contains 80.61% THC, making it a favorite for those who are seeking euphoria without feeling overwhelmed. The stimulating effects of Lemon Haze typically last for up to three hours before easing into a mellow state of repose. This strain is popular with seasoned cannabis consumers, particularly those living with depression.

data.name: Potters Cart
data.desc:
Quality begins on the farm, and Potters Cannabis Co. knows this full well. They start with the finest cannabis flowers with stable genetics, cultivated by master growers with years of experience. Those buds grow up to reach their ideal genetic potential before being harvested for extraction. Processing carries out the same level of quality control and care as the farm. With ethanol extraction (a safer and cleaner extraction than butane and propane) Potters Cannabis Co. combines Live Resin cannabinoids and terpenes from the plant. The extraction artists never use harmful cutting agents, and there is no MCT or coconut oil in their vapes. Post extraction the cannabis oil is formulated with natural terpenes and encased in a C-Cell cartridge with a ceramic coil to create an authentic cannabis experience. Screw it on to any 510 thread battery, although we recommend pairing it with a Potters battery for best results.

Overview
From terpenes to distillate, Potters ensures that every compound is 100% natural. They have always been, and will continue to be, pesticide free, solvent free and microbial free.

A robust profile of over 50 organic terpenes to replicate the natural flower experience. The effects of cannabis are magnified by all of the compounds (cannabinoids + terpenes) working together.. also known as the Entourage Effect.

data.name: Raw Garden Cart

Raw Garden creates clean and accessible cannabis products for everyone. We merge our expertise in farming and biotechnology to produce superior flowers in one of the world’s premiere agricultural regions. Our team consists of multi-generational farmers, nerdy scientists, and heady enthusiasts all devoted to organic farming and bringing clean cannabis to you. We are your trusted single source.

data.name: Tank
data.desc:
Supherb is a lifestyle brand dedicated to revolutionizing the cannabis industry with a pioneering approach that combines state-of-the-art technology with a user-friendly airflow adjustment to provide a luxurious vaping experience. Our new technology allows us to create a pocket-sized, draw-activated vape pen while keeping the power necessary to produce a silky smooth vape cloud. All that power and a system that focuses on adjustable air filtration and not the heat source which eliminates overheating, potency issues, while preserving the flavor you desire. What does all that mean?

That means you can manually adjust the airflow setting anywhere between a quick sneaky toke or a hit that leaves you totally lifted. When you combine our battery, with our lab-tested, artisanal blended cannabis cartridges, you will experience a Supherb vaping experience. All products are tested by Encore Labs and accompanied by a holographic sticker so you can be sure that you are getting the Supherb quality you deserve.

This flavor-packed hybrid brings a euphoric and energetic high that won't leave you hanging.

products.name: Birthday Cake
products.desc:
Supherb Tank (1g) - Birthday Cake
Supherb has another way for you to have your birthday cake and eat it too! Birthday Cake is an Indica-dominant hybrid that is the perfect way to end your day. The 3x distilled concentrate is a proprietary blend that delivers a smoother, richer throat hit with no embarrassing cough.

products.name: Blue Dream
products.desc:
Supherb Tank (1g) - Blue Dream
This highly effective strain is the cross of DJ short Blueberry and the Santa Cruz Haze. With a sweet berry aroma hint of its Blueberry origin, Blue Dream ensures relief without inflicting heavy sedative effects. Blue Dream's high is all the best parts of its parentage wrapped neatly into a flavor-packed, beautifully balanced package. This well rounded Sativa dominant hybrid will keep you on a consistently mellow but creative and effective high that truly has "legs."

data.name: Tree Base Klear Cart
data.desc:
Tree Base Klear is founded on the ultimate power of truth. Truth in their process, products, and company.

Overview
High quality oil starts from high quality plant extracts, and that's where Tree Base Klear starts. We then utilize proprietary refinement techniques in a multi-step process that selectively removes major plant contaminants from the oil including chlorophyll, plant lipids, proteins and carbohydrates. An added benefit of this refinement process is a water clear oil with amazing optical clarity.

Our oil is not just thc distillate, it is a full spectrum cannabis extract. While our refinement process removes the majority of plant impurities, important cannabis biomolecules such as phytocannabinoids and terpenoids are retained. Our oil does not contain any additional excipients such as propylene glycol (pg), polyethylene glycol (peg), vegetable glycerin (vg), medium chain triglycerides (mct), or coconut oil.

products.desc: SFV OG - or San Fernando Valley OG - began as a phenotype of OG Kush. A grower named Swerve at Cali Connection Farms in Southern California’s San Fernando Valley bred it with an Afghani from Homegrown Fantaseeds. The resulting strain takes its initials from its parent strain, as well as the abbreviated location of its seed bank.

data.name: West Coast CUREpen
data.desc:
The West Coast Cure team are nonconformists who have been loyal to cannabis since the prohibition days. For decades, they have been hunting and hand-selecting the gassiest strains while fostering relationships with cultivators and innovative wax artists. Winning the first NorCal Cannabis Cup for Concentrates in 2012 was the crowning moment for their brand’s vision.

They aren’t a new market entrant who joined the game after 2018 to make inferior products without a heart. They are West Coast Cure, the hardcore OGs who bring you crazy fire weed.

Overview
High-potency and highly effective, our Premium THC CUREpen Cartridges offer a convenient way to unwind from the modern grind. With a variety of strains to choose from, you can conveniently blow off a little steam in more places where traditional smoking is not tolerated.

Strains
Blueberry Kush, Grape Ape, Strawberry Cream, Banana Smoothie, and Mango Haze.

data.name: Cold Cure Live Rosin T1
data.desc:
Our team has thoroughly investigated the "science of quality" behind the art of hashish and we're extending our meticulous eye for excellence on each and every batch, while keeping it simple. Starting with our freshly frozen award-winning, indoor flower, we gently agitate and collect the ice water hash before pressing into live rosin. Applying low heat and pressure, we allow it to cold-cure for the squad's preferred dabbing consistency. As everyday smokers and lovers of the craft, we are laser focused on putting out the best cannabis products we can. It is our sincere hope you'll enjoy this hash as much as we do, cheers fam!

1st tier - First wash, between 90-120 microns - this represents the best hash we offer, always made in small batches.

data.name: Crushed Diamonds
data.desc:
Raw Garden creates clean and accessible cannabis products for everyone. We merge our expertise in farming and biotechnology to produce superior flowers in one of the world’s premiere agricultural regions. Our team consists of multi-generational farmers, nerdy scientists, and heady enthusiasts all devoted to organic farming and bringing clean cannabis to you. We are your trusted single source.

1 full gram of refined live resin crushed diamonds.

Overview
Crushed Diamonds deliver the same power and purity you’ve come to expect from our original Refined Live Resin™ Diamonds, but in a far more adaptable and versatile format. Crushed Diamonds come perfectly shattered into an easy-to-use crystalline-crumble. It’s a THCa concentrate that moves beyond the dab rig into joints and bowls. The ultra-fine texture means these powerful cannabinoid-crystals are easy to sprinkle onto bowls, roll up into joints, or enjoy with a traditional or cold start dabs.

data.name: Cured Badder
data.desc:
Oakland Extracts learned that success begins with high quality starting material from small, local farms. Over the years they fine-tuned a proprietary technique that allows for maximum terpene retention. Their signature Cookie Crumble wax – and everything we do – focuses on natural flavor and high potency. They never add terps, THC or any other flavorings or additives, and everything they make is single source.

Overview
From Oakland Extract's luscious whipped badders to their delectable sugars, everything they make focuses on natural flavor and high potency. Their process begins with high-grade indoor cannabis which undergoes hydrocarbon extraction at cryogenic temps. From there, their lead extraction artist uses different post processing techniques to make a variety of tasty dabbables.

For decades, they have been hunting and hand-selecting the gassiest strains while fostering relationships with cultivators and innovative wax artists. Winning the first NorCal Cannabis Cup for Concentrates in 2012 was the crowning moment for their brand’s vision.

They aren’t a new market entrant who joined the game after 2018 to make inferior products without a heart. They are West Coast Cure, the hardcore OGs who bring you crazy fire weed.

West Coast Cure’s signature crystalized Diamonds are formed after being capped under 12-15 psi of pressure and 80 degrees for 12 weeks. Loaded with THCA, it offers the elevated dabbers the purest form of cannabis concentrate available on the market today.

data.name: Hashish Lux Temple Ball
data.desc:
The mythical lore of hashish is one of the most mesmerizing and enticing sides of cannabis history. The oldest evidence of cannabis’ psychoactive use was discovered was in the form pressed resin in a Chinese grave dating back 2700 years. From there, hashish has been found from men on the mountain creating their own paradise, to groups getting together to smoke hashish on a hookah.

The act of pressing and aging resin into hashish brings forth a new level of flavor and experience. Don’t let the darker color scare you, this is going to be a smooth smoke. This product is made for those wishing to experience a deeper level of cannabis knowledge. Our facility is equipped with a custom drying and aging room with pristine conditions to do the hard work for you. Our hashish doesn’t come on to the market until it has been aging for a minimum 3 months. This allows it's flavors to meld and create new profiles that we in the cannabis industry are still deciphering.

Once you bring it home, break right in and see for yourself the difference between hash and hashish. Maybe you allow it to rest longer, letting it continue on its aging process undisturbed. Either way, we are looking forward to hearing about your experiences with hashish.

products.name: BlockBerry
products.desc: Blockberry is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Black Cherry Punch and Tropicana Cookies. This strain is 50% sativa and 50% indica. Blockberry has a unique structure and is one of the sturdiest plants you can grow. It produces dense, olive-green buds with purple hues and a thick layer of frosty trichomes. Blockberry is 28% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Leafly customers tell us Blockberry effects include feeling euphoric, creative and focused. Medical marijuana patients often choose Blockberry when dealing with symptoms associated with gastrointestinal disorders, depression, and fibromyalgia. Bred by California’s Blockhead Budz, Blockberry features flavors like orange, vanilla and blue cheese. The dominant terpene of this strain is myrcene, which gives it an earthy and cherry aroma. The average price of Blockberry typically ranges from $40-$60 per eighth. Blockberry is also known as Superboof, a name given by grower Mobile Jay who selected a special variety of this strain.

products.name: Coffee Cream
products.desc: a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Cookies and Cream and Colombian Gold. This strain is a balanced hybrid, blending qualities from both its indica and sativa parent strains. products.name: Gello Shotz

products.name: Tropical Burst
products.desc: Tropical Burst is a 2023 strain bred and released by Seed Junky Genetics that Leafly editor David Downs calls “a perfect Zkittlez.” Tropical Burst is made from a genetic cross of (Orange Push Pop x Banana Cream Cake) x Zkittlez bx2, amplifying classic Z tropical flavors with cream, orange, banana and cake as well as thickening the bud structure and trichome coat. Its tangy flavors precede an intense sativa-focus, giggles and euphoria.

data.name: Live Resin Sauce
data.desc:
The West Coast Cure team are nonconformists who have been loyal to cannabis since the prohibition days. For decades, they have been hunting and hand-selecting the gassiest strains while fostering relationships with cultivators and innovative wax artists. Winning the first NorCal Cannabis Cup for Concentrates in 2012 was the crowning moment for their brand’s vision.

They aren’t a new market entrant who joined the game after 2018 to make inferior products without a heart. They are West Coast Cure, the hardcore OGs who bring you crazy fire weed.

1 gram live resin sauce.

Overview
Live Resin Sauce is popular given its strong aroma and flavor which delivers a different and more complex experience. Over a period of 4-6 weeks, THCa crystalline starts to crash while solvent is slowly removed. High Terpene Extract (HTE) from the same strain is then reintroduced to give it the aroma-packed smell when you pop the lid off the jar.

data.name: Live Resin Sugar Diamonds
data.desc:
Live resin sugar boasts a unique crystalline texture and a potent flavorful profile. This is achieved through a meticulous process that begins with flash-freezing freshly harvested cannabis at its peak. This crucial step preserves the delicate terpenes and cannabinoids.
The frozen plant then undergoes a solvent-based extraction, typically using butane or propane. The solvent dissolves the desired compounds, which are then collected and purged in a vacuum oven to remove any residual solvents.
This careful purging not only ensures a pure and potent product but also creates the distinctive sugary consistency that gives live resin sugar its name. The final result is a concentrate that captures the robust and authentic essence of the original plant's profile.

data.name: Live Rosin T1
data.desc:
Overview
A solventless refinement process that presses the cannabis (hash or flower, all good) between two heated metal plates. Done just right, the results are a gorgeous golden-white or yellow oil or budder. Available in Persy, 1st Press and 2nd Press.

products.name: Bad Apple #7
products.desc:
710 Labs Live Rosin Tier 1 - Bad Apple #7 (1g)
710 uses a solventless refinement process that presses the cannabis between two metal plates. Done just right, the results are a gorgeous golden-white or yellow oil or budder. Bad Apple is a hybrid marijuana strain made by crossing Fatso and Sour Apple Killer that is extremely potent and will make your tastebuds tingle. This rosin has a sweet and sour tartness on the inhale with a nice subtle crisp apple flavor on the back end.

data.name: Live Rosin T2
data.desc: 710 is obsessed with making the richest flavored, pesticide-free, organically fed, small batch, hand-trimmed cannabis on the planet. They are the OGs that hand select and hunt exotic strains from the most renowned breeders, including Landrace single original seeds that took decades to find. There’s a reason 710 flower is renowned industry wide – they never blind source. 710 meticulously grow their flowers in house, with wholly organic inputs, dry and cure it based on density, and trim it by hand to bring you the most opulent, flavor dense nugs on the market.

data.name: Live Rosin T3
data.desc: 710 is obsessed with making the richest flavored, pesticide-free, organically fed, small batch, hand-trimmed cannabis on the planet. They are the OGs that hand select and hunt exotic strains from the most renowned breeders, including Landrace single original seeds that took decades to find. There’s a reason 710 flower is renowned industry wide – they never blind source. 710 meticulously grow their flowers in house, with wholly organic inputs, dry and cure it based on density, and trim it by hand to bring you the most opulent, flavor dense nugs on the market.

data.name: Live Sauce
data.desc:
Raw Garden creates clean and accessible cannabis products for everyone. We merge our expertise in farming and biotechnology to produce superior flowers in one of the world’s premiere agricultural regions. Our team consists of multi-generational farmers, nerdy scientists, and heady enthusiasts all devoted to organic farming and bringing clean cannabis to you. We are your trusted single source.

1 full gram of live sauce.

Overview
Made from our Clean Green Certified cannabis flower using organically-based farming techniques. Raw Garden cryogenically flash-freezes the flower at harvest in order to preserve the plant’s unique cannabinoid and terpene profiles. Contains approximately 7-14% terpenes and comes in a wetter consistency than Raw Garden Live Resin.

data.name: Persy Water Hash
data.desc:
What is Water Hash? As we stated in our solventless post, in order to make Water Hash, plants are broken down into smaller bud sites and added to large tubs of very cold (almost freezing) water and ice. The plants are then gently stirred. In a cold room, we gently wash the water hash by hand using a paddle, whereas some Hashmakers are using machines to agitate the plants. The gentle agitation at cold temperatures separates the trichome heads from the trichome stalks.
The intent is to keep the heads fully intact without rupturing the membrane and letting the good stuff(resin) drain out. The trichome heads are now floating and hanging out in the vessel of cold water and ice. We then filter that water thru mesh @icextract bags with different micron screen sizes. Each bag is a different size micron ranging from 25ū to 180ū and these bags catch different size trichome heads as well as some stalks and other plant matter. We feel the 90ū - 150ū bags catch the juiciest most valuable trichome heads.

If they melt perfectly on the banger, nail or insert, we release them as fullmelt water hash OR send to our Persy collection of rosin.

data.name: Piatella Extract
data.desc:
Introducing Piatella: the art of artisan hash. Piatella is a specialty artisan hash that exemplifies precision and dedication in every step of its creation.

Crafted from fresh frozen bubble hash, it undergoes a meticulous freeze-drying and cold-curing process, carefully controlled over an extended period.

By minimizing oxygen exposure during curing, Piatella preserves the delicate terpenes that contribute to the unique flavors, aromas, and effects of each strain.

data.name: Solventless Hash Live Rosin
data.desc:
Here at DabLogic our purpose is to cultivate the good life, which is why growing in living soil, hand trimming our buds & packaging our products in sustainable packaging is so important to us! We believe everyone should have access to the best cannabis and cannabis concentrates, so we won't compromise on our cultivation methods. It's not the easiest or least expensive way to grow great cannabis, but we believe it is the best.

Only the most pristine & exquisite flower from the Verde Natural garden are selected to be transformed into DabLogic handmade solventless hashish. This intense dedication to quality and belief in the healing power of plant medicine, produces a live resin that is unrivaled by the competition. By only using old school ice water hash techniques and pressing methods with low heat and pressure we make the best expressions of cannabis in hash form, with no fillers, cutting agents or toxic chemicals. Come experience our divine magical trichomes.

Overview
DabLogic Live Rosin is some of the finest hashish on the market. They use only water, ice, and low heat and pressure to create our solventless/live rosin products. No fillers, no cutting agents, and no toxic solvents.

Volume
1 gram.

products.name: Tropical Oasis
products.desc:
With its perfumy oranges and cream aroma and floral fruity flavor, Tropical Oasis will whisk you away to an island paradise with one taste. An energetic and euphoric high, it's good for outdoor adventures or drifting into daydreams.

Nose: a perfumy oranges and cream citrus hits the nose with a touch of gas.
Taste: floral and slightly fruity with a potent herbal bite.

products.name: White Peach
products.desc: White Peach is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Alien Cookies and Columbian x Starfighter. This strain is 40% sativa and 60% indica. White Peach is a smooth and balanced strain that can provide a relaxing and euphoric high. White Peach effects include feeling focused, happy, and calm. Medical marijuana patients often choose White Peach when dealing with symptoms associated with anxiety, pain, and stress. Bred by Cuban Crew, White Peach features flavors like citrus, clove, and mint. The dominant terpene of this strain is terpinolene, which gives it a fruity and floral aroma.

products.name: Beloved B
products.desc:
Unlock a wave of happy vibes with Beloved B. This blissful rosin, bursting with juicy stone fruits and creamy banana, delivers a smooth, instant lift. Take a hit and be greeted by a vibrant explosion of pomegranate and a hint of bubblegum. Beloved B awakens your senses and might just leave you craving a sweet treat!

Genetics: Strawnana x Pria
Nose: An herbal aroma with a hint of pine and fruit candy.
Taste: Beloved B has a bright Fruity and banana cream flavor with a berry bubble gum finish.

products.name: Durban Sherbet
products.desc:
A delicious and terp-forward cross of a Sunset Sherbert and a Mendocino f7 Landrace Durban, Durban Sherbet delivers a powerful punch with smooth creamy fruit flavors and a touch of citrus and skunk. Instantly lifted, one puff can send you into orbit! But the high mellows out into an uplifting and creative ride.

Genetics: Bag Seed Sunset Sherbert X Mendocino f7 Landrace Durban

Nose: bright terps that jump out at you when sniffed, Durban Sherbert smells creamy like peaches or papaya, with a piney hint of spice, a touch of citrus and a little skunky stank.
Taste: at first inhale, Durban Sherbet vapor has a bit of an astringent bite. A full, herbal flavor with a mix of fruit and a touch of skunk fills your taste buds as you enjoy the dab and exhale.

products.name: Moroccan Peaches
products.desc:
With unique genetics, Moroccan Peaches is a light blonde and dense Whipped Rosin with a fruity flavor reminiscent of summer stone fruit. It has a bit of a spicy bite that hits strong and quickly envelops you as you drift into a dreamy euphoria that will surely elevate your mood.

Genetics: Spanish Barbara x Lemon Tree Skorange

Nose: light and fruity, a whiff of Moroccan Peaches is a pungent reminder of summer stone fruit, with a bit of a spicy kush bite.
Taste: Moroccan Peaches is aptly named, at first taste the peach flavor really comes through, cut by a slightly skunky and spicy bite with a touch of citrus thrown in.

products.name: Sour Peaches
products.desc:
Another masterpiece of genetics, Sour Peaches is deliciously fruity and floral with a piney herbal edge. It hits quickly and leaves you stimulated, creative, and floating in the clouds.

Genetics: Moroccan Peaches x AJ's Sour D
Nose: a deep whiff of Sour Peaches brings out citrus fruit and light floral flavors that make you salivate with anticipation.
Taste: the first hit is tangy, piney and herbal, with a floral flavor that lingers as the vapor dissipates. The flavor is lightly peachy with a bit of gas, a nod to its sour diesel roots.

products.name: Virya
products.desc:
One puff of Virya delivers a piney citrus flavor and an instant uplifting high. A nice mix of floral, fruit and pungent gas flavors, this strain will leave you light on your feet with not a worry in sight.

Genetics: Sherb bx x Key Lime Chem x Pria
Nose: piney and a bit floral, a whiff of Virya delivers a light sweetness tampered with a pungent bite of ammonia.
Taste: an inhale quickly delivers a piney citrus taste, followed by a mellower fruity and floral flavor that maintains a spicy edge.

products.name: Zhem Pai
products.desc:
Zhem Pai instantly awakens the senses with an astringent bite and mellows out into floral herbal flavors and a mellow, floaty high. The perfect lift to ease into your day.

Genetics: Z x Keylime Pie x Chemdog

Nose: floral with a strong ammonia bite that has hints of funk and pine.
Taste: slightly herbal and peppery, with a pungent astringent bite on the inhale.

products.name: C. Jack
products.desc:
C. Jack is a heavyweight on the west coast thanks to its Jack Herer lineage. Known as a sativa with powerful cerebral effects, the strain is sought after by creatives and anyone seeking an elevated mental experience. The effects tend to take effect fairly quickly, and are most commonly described as energizing, euphoric, and creative.

For medical users, C. Jack has been used to help relieve symptoms such as nausea, poor appetite, headaches and depression. It is typically ideal for daytime use because of its energetic properties, although for some users it is a helpful nighttime companion.

products.name: Cosmic Glue
products.desc:
Cosmic Glue’s effects are fast-acting, delivering a strong, heady euphoria that isn’t for the faint of heart. This strain lives up to its reputation with its pungent, long-lasting effects, often sparking intense creativity, a trait inherited from its Space Queen parent.

Thanks to its other famous parent, G.G. #4, Cosmic Glue also brings a powerful body relaxation, making it more sedating than uplifting. Ideal for evening use, medical users frequently turn to Cosmic Glue to reduce stress, pain, and muscle spasms.

products.name: Purple Punch
products.desc:
Purple Punch certainly lives up to its name with potent effects, making it ideal for experienced cannabis users. Expect a deep, full-body relaxation that soothes tired muscles, while your mind unwinds and melts away stress in a warm embrace of cannabinoids, led by THC. With our new rechargeable All-In-One device, you can enjoy every moment of relaxation with the added convenience of recharging for extended use.

For medicinal purposes, Purple Punch is well-known for relieving anxiety, racing thoughts, insomnia, and muscle or joint pain. Its sedative effects make this indica vape pen perfect for bedtime or whenever you have the time to fully decompress and rest. Now available in a device that offers longer sessions and effortless charging, it’s ready whenever you are.

data.desc: Cultivated by a team of dedicated, diverse professionals, Dabwoods is an experienced organization with roots in quality control, hardware manufacturing, and product excellence, leading the cannabis industry forward.

products.name: Blue Dream
products.desc: Dabwood Disposables (1g) - Blue Dream </br>Blue Dream is a popular sativa strain that is known to energize and stimulate the mind, great for people looking for a creative spark. Blue dream has a flavor profile of sweet mixed berries accented by an earthy floral scent.

products.name: Georgia Peach
products.desc: Dabwood Disposables (1g) - Georgia Peach </br>Georgia Peach is a fan-favorite indica strain that won best vape disposable at Kushstock Festival in 2022. Its rich and peachy flavor complements the sweet and fruity aroma the strain emits. The effects of Georgia Peach include a strong body-high that can boost spirits and minimize feelings of anxiety or tension.

products.name: Pineapple Kush
products.desc: Dabwood Disposables (1g) - Pineapple Kush </br>Pineapple Kush is a hybrid strain that may produce uplifting and mellowing effects, great for people looking to destress. This strain has a distinct tropical aroma and a flavor profile that combines pineapple and mint with hints of caramel.

products.name: Sunset Tsunami
products.desc: Dabwood Disposables (1g) - Sunset Tsunami</br>Sunset Tsunami is a sativa strain crossing Sunset Sherbet and Sour Tsunami. This strain produces a delicious aroma and has a fruity flavor profile that expresses notes of pineapple, mango, and strawberry. Sunset Tsunami offers a calming high that can relieve symptoms of stress and tension without the sedative effects.

products.name: Trainwreck
products.desc: Dabwood Disposables (1g) - Trainwreck </br>Trainwreck is a sativa strain known for producing potent effects that hits you like a bullet. The aromas are reminiscent of lemon and pine accompanied with a subtle spice to its taste. This strain promotes feelings of happiness that can put you in an inspiring mood.

products.name: Watermelon Z
products.desc: Dabwood Disposables (1g) - Watermelon Z</br>Watermelon Z is an indica strain. Indicative of its name, the strain has a distinct watermelon taste with a candy-like finish. The relaxing effects of Watermelon Z are as pleasant as its sweet aroma, making it useful as a sleeping aid or appetite stimulant.

products.name: Apple Gelato Ice
products.desc: Apple Gelato ICE is a strain that delights the senses with its sweet and refreshing apple flavor. The taste is reminiscent of biting into a crisp and juicy apple, accompanied by a creamy undertone. This strain provides a balanced and relaxing experience, perfect for unwinding and enjoying the fruity essence. Apple Gelato ICE is an excellent choice for those seeking a flavorful and soothing cannabis option.

products.name: Cali Gas OG
products.desc: Cali Gas OG offers a unique flavor experience that combines fuel-like notes with a citrusy twist. The taste is characterized by a pungent and earthy flavor profile with hints of lemon and lime. This strain delivers a potent and uplifting high, providing an energizing and focused experience. Cali Gas OG is an excellent choice for those seeking a flavorful and invigorating cannabis strain.

products.name: Cherry Grapefruit
products.desc: Cherry Grapefruit is a strain that combines the best of both fruity worlds, offering a unique and enjoyable flavor experience. The taste is a perfect balance of sweet cherries and tangy grapefruit, creating a mouth-watering sensation. This strain provides a euphoric and uplifting high that enhances mood and promotes a sense of well-being. Cherry Grapefruit is an excellent choice for those seeking a flavorful and invigorating cannabis option.

products.name: Jack Herer
products.desc: Jack Herer is a strain that offers a unique and distinct flavor profile. It combines earthy, piney, and citrusy notes, creating a complex and invigorating taste. Known for its uplifting and energizing effects, Jack Herer promotes creativity and focus. If you're looking for a strain that delivers a flavorful experience with an invigorating high, Jack Herer is the perfect choice.

products.name: Super Sour Diesel
products.desc: Super Sour Diesel is a strain renowned for its strong and pungent flavor profile. It offers an intense combination of diesel fuel and citrusy sourness, creating a unique and memorable taste. This strain delivers an energetic and uplifting high, stimulating creativity and focus. If you're looking for a strain that packs a punch in both flavor and effects, Super Sour Diesel is an excellent option.

products.name: Wedding Cake
products.desc: Wedding Cake is a strain known for its rich and indulgent flavor profile that resembles a delectable dessert. The taste is reminiscent of vanilla cake with sweet and creamy undertones. This strain provides a relaxing and euphoric experience, making it a popular choice for celebrations and special occasions. If you're looking for a strain that combines a delicious taste with a blissful high, Wedding Cake is the perfect choice.

Can’t decide which path to take? You don’t have to. Leave the toggle in the middle to blend both strains for one sensational output. Two hits at this level will guarantee a high score.

products.name: Blueberry Kush + Lemon Headz
products.desc: Explore the enticing mix of Blueberry Kush and Lemon Headz, blending the calm sweetness of blueberries with the refreshing tang of lemons. This duo creates a balanced experience, transitioning smoothly from relaxation to invigoration, ideal for a diverse and stimulating flavor journey.

products.name: Cactus Cooler + Tropic Thunder
products.desc: Experience the ultimate adventure with Tropic Thunder and Cactus Kooler. Tropic Thunder bursts with bold tropical fruit punch and zesty citrus, while Cactus Kooler delivers a refreshing mix of quenching orange and pineapple, perfect for taming your desert thirst. Switch between the two with a flick, or combine them for a bold yet refreshing fusion.

products.name: Kiwi OG + Guava Diesel
products.desc: Dive into the harmonious blend of Kiwi OG and Guava Diesel, uniting the serene sweetness of kiwis with the vibrant zest of guava. This pair crafts a nuanced experience, seamlessly shifting from peaceful relaxation to lively stimulation, perfect for a multifaceted and exhilarating flavor adventure.

products.name: Mango Sunset + Orange Crush
products.desc: Enjoy the vibrant fusion of Mango Sunset and Orange Crush, combining the smooth sweetness of mangoes with the crisp tang of oranges. This blend creates a seamless transition from relaxing mango richness to invigorating citrus zest, ideal for a lively, citrus-forward adventure.

products.name: Peach Driver + Watermelon Mimosa
products.desc: Get ready for a powerhouse flavor combo with Peach Driver and Watermelon Mimosa, two standout hybrids from our AIO line. Peach Driver delivers a smooth, juicy punch of ripe peaches, while Watermelon Mimosa brings the crisp, bubbly sweetness of watermelon with a hint of citrus sparkle. Enjoy each on its own or mix them together!

products.name: Strawberry Fields + Pineapple Express
products.desc: Indulge in the fusion of Strawberry Fields and Pineapple Express, a blend that moves from the sweet calm of strawberries to the vibrant zing of pineapples. This combination offers a journey from peaceful berry serenity to lively tropical excitement.

data.name: Essentials Live Resin Disposable
data.desc: High quality, high potency, LIVE RESIN in a 1 Gram disposable vape bar. Super convenient and ready to use! Micro-USB rechargeable battery for the slow smoker. Sauce Bar even has a built-in window so that you can see your remaining oil.

products.name: Alien Runtz
products.desc: One of our breakout hits for 2023. This strain is positively stoned in crystals. At first, the buds look just like Alien Mints, with the same coloring and tight bud structure, but then you notice the heavy sugar dusting from the Runtz. Their sweet, minty flavors transform into a wonderfully warm high that most people find carries a double helping of upbeat relaxation.

products.name: Aloha Express
products.desc: Aloha is a sativa strain that leaves users with an upbeat, energetic buzz that may also be helpful in treating pain such as migraines. Aloha Express aromas are that of grass and citrus that brings a fresh experience similar to an island getaway. Its sativa effects can be a little much for some users, so those who are looking for less mental stimulation should be wary.

products.name: Animal Mintz
products.desc: Animal Mintz is the offspring of Animal Cookies and SinMint Cookies. This indica leaning hybrid is ideal for combatting symptoms associated with stress. The potent body high of Animal Mintz will have pain and anxiety float away, leaving consumers feeling relaxed and euphoric.

products.name: Apple Fritter
products.desc: Apple Fritter, a true hybrid strain, is known for its powerful and relaxing high. Put out by Lumpy’s Flowers, Apple Fritter is a strain with secret origins. Those who enjoy Apple Fritter say this strain allows you to enjoy an evening without losing your cool. Apple Fritter has a flavor aroma that comes off as sweet and earthy, with a light cheesy apple pastry influence. This strain induces a great happy, uplifted, and relaxed high throughout the day.

products.name: Blue Cookies
products.desc: Blue Cookies is an indica-dominant hybrid that originated from a cross between Blueberry and Girl Scout Cookies (GSC). Known for its high potency and sweet and fruity aroma, this strain has been reported to taste like blueberries and citrus. It’s been reported to give a head high initially, followed by a relaxing body high.

products.name: Blueberry Kush
products.desc: Blueberry Kush is an indica strain made by crossing Blueberry and OG Kush. This strain produces effects that slowly bring on a heavy body sensation, aiding in relieving stress and promoting full-body relaxation. Blueberry Kush is the ultimate couch lock strain for the evening time that will send you into the deepest of sleep.

products.name: Gelato
products.desc: Gelato, aka Larry Bird, is a hybrid strain made by crossing Sunset Sherbet and Thin Mint Girl Scout Cookies. The effects of Gelato produce a euphoric high accompanied by strong feelings of relaxation. Consumers say the physical sensation comes on strong, but many find themselves still mentally agile enough to stay productive and creative during the day. Gelato gets its name from the fruity dessert-like aroma it smells similar to.

products.name: Gelonade
products.desc:
Gelonade is a hybrid marijuana strain made by crossing Lemon Tree with

Gelato #41. Gelonade produces tingly and uplifting affects. that will make you feel like a social butterfly. This strain features mostly sweet flavors like fruity citrus and vanilla.

products.name: Ghost Train Haze
products.desc: First bred by Rare Dankness, Ghost Train Haze is a sativa cross of Ghost OG and Neville’s Wreck. With a sour citrus and floral aroma, Ghost Train Haze delivers a potent dose of THC to knock out pain, depression, and appetite loss. Note that some patients who may be prone to anxiety should be cautious of this heavy-hitter. Low doses are conducive to concentration and creativity, but you may notice some cerebral haziness as you smoke more. Overall Ghost Train Haze is a suitable strain for an uplifted and energetic high.

products.name: GrandDaddy Purp
products.desc: Grandaddy Purp is a famous indica cross of Purple Urkle and Big Bud. This California staple inherits a complex grape and berry aroma from its Purple Urkle parent. Its potent effects are clearly detectable in both mind and body, delivering a fusion of cerebral euphoria and physical relaxation. While your thoughts may float in a dreamy buzz, your body is more likely to find itself fixed in one spot for the duration of GDP’s effects. Granddaddy Purple is typically consumed to combat pain, stress, insomnia, appetite loss, and muscle spasms.

products.name: Gushers
products.desc: Gushers is a popular sativa strain. Ideal for combating symptoms associated with stress and anxiety.

products.name: Ice Cream Mintz
products.desc: Ice Cream Mintz, also known as Ice Cream Mints, is an indica weed strain. Effects include hungry, giggly, and happy.

products.name: Jack Diesel
products.desc: Jack Diesel is a power house sativa born from crossing Jack Herer and NYC Diesel. The effects of Jack Diesel produce a clear-headed, creative and blissful high; a perfect accompaniment for socializing or being active. While delivering a cerebral euphoria, your body will gently ease into a deeply relaxed state. Its aroma is that of diesel and herb with a hint of sweet banana. Consumers use this strain to help combat anxiety, alleviate pain, and fight inflammation throughout their day without fatigue.

products.name: Kings Kush
products.desc: King’s Kush is an indica strain made by crossing OG Kush with Grape. King’s Kush produces gradual, yet powerful effects that will make you feel relaxed and euphoric. This strain features a flavor profile that is similar to a tangy grape with undertones of lavender. King’s Kush is a great choice to relieve symptoms associated with insomnia.

products.name: NYC Sour

Taste: Fruity, Sour, Candy
