products.name: Space Octane
products.desc: This sweet and fruity strain will have you in outer space in no time, with an uplift that’s coupled with relaxation. You’ll feel long term relief, but not comatose or couch locked. This strain has high potency and brings a burst of happiness. Space Octane is an excellent pain reliever and stress reducer.

products.name: Strawberry Cough
products.desc: Known for its sweet smell of fresh strawberries and its expanding sensation that can make even the most seasoned consumer cough. Strawberry Cough is a potent sativa straing with mysterious genetic origins. This profile is thought to be a cross of Strawberry Fields and Haze. The skunky, berry flavors will capture your senses while the cerebral, uplifting effects provide an aura of euphoria that is sure to leave a smile on your face. Strawberry Cough is a great solution in times of elevated stress.

products.name: White Widow
products.desc: Among the most famous strains worldwide is White Widow, a balanced hybrid first bred in the Netherlands by Green House Seeds. A cross between a Brazilian sativa landrace and a resin-heavy South Indian indica, White Widow has blessed every Dutch coffee shop menu since its birth in the 1990s. A powerful burst of euphoria and energy breaks through immediately, stimulating both conversation and creativity.

products.name: Zkittles
products.desc: Zkittlez is an indica-dominant mix of Grape Ape and Grapefruit that is crossed with an undisclosed strain to produce a candy-flavored profile bred by 3rd Gen Family and Terp Hogz. The effects of Zkittlez are calming, leaving consumers focused, alert, and happy while simultaneously relaxing the body to help unwind any time of day.

products.name: Grape God
products.desc: Grape God is an indica-dominant hybrid that combines God Bud and Grapefruit genetics. As its name suggests, this strain has a sweet grape aroma with earthy notes that activate on the exhale.

products.name: Herc Haze
products.desc: The "Herc Haze" strain, often referring to strains with Hercules in their name like "Hercules," is a cross between Gupta Kush and Hawaiian Urkle. It's a sativa-dominant hybrid known for its high THC content and uplifting effects, often used for physical activity.

products.name: Lemon Lighting
products.desc: Lemon Lightening is a sativa strain created through crossing the potent Super Lemon Haze and AK-47 strains. Lemon Lightening is the perfect choice for patients who want a hard hitting bud.

products.name: Snake Eyes
products.desc: The Snake Eyes strain genetics are a cross between Bubba Skywalker and Phoenix OG (male). It was developed in Los Angeles' Arts District in 2014.

products.name: Strawberry Kiss Kush
products.desc: Strawberry Kiss Kush is sweet, strong and truly well-rounded. This strain certainly justifies its lineage and contains a musky candy strawberry taste. It is essentially found as a cross between OG Kush and the sugary Strawberry Cough and is mostly strong but not overwhelming.

products.name: Sunshine OG
products.desc: Sunshine OG is a sativa-dominant hybrid created by crossing Chemdawg with Sunshine Daydream. This strain offers vibrant citrus and tropical flavors with earthy undertones. Known for its uplifting and focusing effects, Sunshine OG delivers a balanced experience that promotes happiness and relaxation, making it a versatile choice for daytime activities.

products.name: Watermelon Wave
products.desc: Watermelon Wave is an indica strain created through crossing the potent Mother of Berries, Tidal Wave, and Diesel Kush strains. If you’re searching for a potent bud with a great fruity flavor to go along with it, Watermelon Wave is definitely made for you.

products.name: Gush Mintz
products.desc: Gush Mints, a potent hybrid, is a remarkable creation of Kush Mints with a blend of F1 Durb and Gushers, combining the best traits of multiple beloved Cookies family strains. Gush Mints boasts a tantalizing profile of gassy and sweet terpenes, complemented by subtle piney notes. Prepare for a body-melting high that soothes the mind, leaving you in a state of pure relaxation. While productivity may take a back seat, you'll undoubtedly feel fantastic throughout the experience.

products.name: OG Kush
products.desc: OG Kush is a premium quality Indica strain, known for its sweet and pungent aroma. This strain is a cross between Black Domina and Critical Mass, resulting in a relaxing and sedative high. The effects of OG Kush are long-lasting and include a strong body buzz, making it ideal for stress relief and insomnia.

products.name: Sour Diesel
products.desc: Sour Diesel is crafted with single strain cannabis-derived terpenes which produce immense flavor and inspire energy, focus and motivation. Perfect for when you need that extra pick-me-up. On top of being a great indica to unwind, its euphoric effects will brighten your overall mood.

products.name: Super Lemon Haze
products.desc: Super Lemon Haze, or SLH, is a potent sativa that has earned its reputation as a two-time Cannabis Cup winner. It is a fusion of Lemon Skunk and Super Silver Haze, delivering on its promise of lemony goodness. With a zesty, citrusy, and slightly sweet aroma, the taste mirrors its namesake, reminiscent of tart and sweet lemonhead candy. What sets Super Lemon Haze apart are its unique effects, which provide an energetic and lively experience. This strain is an ideal choice for those seeking a burst of vibrant energy and creativity.

products.name: Moroccan Peaches
products.desc:
Cultivated by Bandwagon Gardens, an outdoor farm in northeastern Humboldt west of Willow Creek, nestled in the hills where Humbodlt meets Trinity County. This regenerative farm utilizes live soil, homemade compost tea and hugelkultur raised beds to create the ideal environment for producing the full-term plants we use for our concentrates.

Bred by Purple City Genetics, Moroccan Peaches is a tantalizing blend of Spanish Barbara and Lemon Tree Skorange. Its mesmerizing terpene profile is a mix of peachy incense and citrusy lemon gas, delivering a wave of calming euphoria that melts your worries away.

products.name: Strawberry Banana
products.desc:
Cultivated by Clear Water Farms - Homegrown under the Humboldt Sun. The Clear Water Farms is a member of the Uplift Co-operative which is owned entirely by independent legacy farmers and was the first cannabis cooperative post-legalization. Its mission is to ensure the success and viability of Mattole Valley's small cannabis farms so you can taste the traditional flavor of artisanal, Humboldt buds.

Strawberry Banana is an Indica-leaning hybrid between two fruity strains: Bubble Gum and Banana Kush with a universally appealing flavor and an easygoing, mellow high.

products.name: Lemon Cherry Gelato
products.desc: Lemon Cherry Gelato is a sativa-dominant strain that offers a zesty and invigorating experience. Its uplifting effects promote energy, euphoria, and enhanced focus, making it ideal for creative endeavors. The aroma is a combination of refreshing citrus and sweet cherries, while the flavor profile delivers a zesty lemon taste with creamy undertones. It's a perfect choice for those seeking a fruity and uplifting sativa strain.

products.name: Mango Madness
products.desc: Mango Madness is a well-balanced hybrid strain that combines the best of both indica and sativa genetics. Its effects offer a harmonious blend of cerebral stimulation and physical relaxation, making it suitable for any time of day. The aroma is characterized by a distinct mango sweetness, and the flavor profile features a fusion of mango and citrus with a touch of earthiness. Enjoy the smooth smoke and balanced experience of Mango Madness.

products.name: Paradise Punch OG
products.desc: Paradise Punch OG is a potent indica strain that induces deep relaxation and tranquility. With its calming euphoria, it is best enjoyed in the evening for unwinding and stress relief. The aroma is a delightful mix of sweet tropical notes, reminiscent of a fruity punch. If you're looking for a strain that promotes serenity and contentment, Paradise Punch OG is an excellent choice.

products.name: Strawberry Dream
products.desc: Strawberry Dream is a delightful hybrid strain that combines the uplifting qualities of sativa with the relaxing effects of indica. It offers a gentle cerebral high that promotes euphoria and a soothing body buzz for physical comfort. The aroma is sweet and fruity, reminiscent of fresh strawberries, and the flavor profile is a burst of strawberry sweetness with subtle floral undertones. If you're seeking a balanced and flavorful hybrid strain, Strawberry Dream is the perfect choice.

products.name: Super Silver Haze
products.desc: Super Silver Haze is a legendary sativa strain known for its energizing and uplifting effects. With a THC-rich profile, it delivers a cerebral buzz that boosts focus, creativity, and motivation. The aroma is a delightful mix of sweet, earthy, and citrusy notes, leaving a refreshing aftertaste. This strain is perfect for daytime use when you need a mood lift and a burst of productivity.

products.name: Grapefruit Kush
products.desc:
Kurvana’s Grapefruit Kush strain is the creative All-In-One vape you’ve been seeking. A classic kush that hails from the Afghani Kush family, it offers uplifting cerebral effects with a burst of citrus flavor. Made by crossing BC Kush and Grapefruit, this sativa-dominant hybrid offers a deliciously sweet and tangy candied grapefruit flavor profile that is unmatched in the world of cannabis.

The original flower from which this cannabis oil was extracted is fully present in the final product, from the pleasant hash-like aftertaste to the full spectrum of terpenes. Limonene and beta-caryophyllene combine to give this legendary kush its citrusy aromatics with hints of sweet pepper in the background.

Our Grapefruit Kush All-In-One is ready to use with no additional battery or charging required. Perfect for when you’re on the go!

products.name: Jack Herer
products.desc:
Jack Herer is the strain that cannabis legends are made of. This award-winning, timeless sativa hybrid has roots that go back to 1990s-era Netherlands where it was once a popular medical-grade strain. Its iconic history and well-known capacity for sparking creative energy keep Jack Herer one of the most sought-after names in the cannabis world. 

Kurvana’s own All-In-One Jack Herer vape is a potent, full-spectrum premium cannabis oil that allows its natural herbaceous and rich spicy aromatics to shine. You’ll feel an instant boost in mood and energy upon inhalation as your senses are rewarded with the flavor and aroma of pine, sage, and a splash of citrus. Part of our Originals line, we have preserved all of the extraordinary terpenes and cannabinoids of this legendary strain in a full-spectrum cannabis oil. 

Kurvana’s All-In-One Jack Herer cartridge is ready to use with no additional battery or charging required.

products.name: Master OG
products.desc:
The Master OG strain, also known as “Master OG Kush” is an indica-dominant hybrid that was made by crossing Master Kush and Empress Kush. This stress-busting All-In-One indica vape is considered a classic staple among cannabis enthusiasts who relish its familiar diesel scent that carries a splash of citrus and rich earth. It offers a smooth vaping experience that still tickles the palate with a bit of spice, thanks to its OG lineage. If you enjoy OG strains, Master OG is master of them all, and boasts a medium-high potency that is just right.

Master OG All-In-One is ready to use with no additional battery or charging required.

products.name: FKAFL
products.desc:
The Soap x L.A. Rouge
HYBRID
If you know, you know. FKAFL is a masterful, award-winning cross of our L.A. Rouge and The Soap, offering a flavor profile that is as complex as it is refined. The buds present a veritable feast for the eyes, with a multicolored plumy structure draped in a layer of white velvet trichomes. Upon opening the jar, a sweet, inviting sensation of citrus and diesel entices the nose and deepens with each inhale. A fusion of subtle nuances similar to rosemary, red fruit, and hints of cheese create a savory charcuterie-like experience, followed by a smooth, lavender-rich exhale that cleanses the palate. Like the classic pairing of fine wine with artisanal cheese, this sophisticated Hybrid is a true sensory delight and is ideal for those seeking a euphoric, indulgent sense of serenity.

products.name: Orange Sapphire
products.desc:
Orange Bellini x Blue Lotus
SATIVA

Discover one of our most precious gems yet, the award-winning Sativa, Orange Sapphire. This jewel is a rare Orange Bellini and Blue Lotus cross, boasting a multifaceted flavor and aroma profile. Breaking apart the glistening indigo buds releases a captivating scent of orange zest, mixed berries, and an air of diesel, which evolves into a warm, floral breath that imparts a rich, silky sweetness on the palate.

products.name: Sour Sangria
products.desc:
Sour Sangria is an award-winning Sativa with a sophisticated flavor profile and well-balanced high. This compelling cross of our own Yuzu Mac and Pandora makes for dense, resinous nugs that display vivid blue and Fuschia tones. Its sweet, sour, and citrus-forward nose translates to a refreshing inhale, while floral, earthy, and peppery notes make for a bold exhalation. While this high can have calming and reflective qualities, its uplifting nature keeps the mind sharp, focused, and engaged. INDICA

Panta Rhei is a dynamic cross of our Blue Agape #9 and Oro, with midnight purple buds, fiery orange hairs, and glimmering trichomes resembling the brink of twilight. This strain's evolution in flavor and aroma embodies the ancient Greek philosophy "everything flows," offering a journey of sensory expansion that shifts from sweet, gentle earth tones into a resonant blend of evergreen, citrus fruit, and gas. This transformative Indica is an ode to the beauty of change and encourages one to find the balance between stillness and movement.

Drink straight, chilled or mix in other beverages such as soda water or flavored beverages. It is very versatile so you can get creative with it. Also a good party favor--use the whole bottle to make a party punch or pour a little into your friends' cups (not secretly!). DOSING

This is a very strong beverage so please use with caution. 10 servings (1 capful) per bottle. data.name: RSO
data.desc: 710 Labs RSO is a decarboxylated full spectrum extract. RSO is short for Rick Simpson Oil (also commonly referred to as "FSO" for Full Spectrum Extract), meaning it contains all the cannabinoids, terpenes, and many other valuable compounds found in the cannabis plant. We hope that the interaction of all the compounds of the plant, all concentrated together in this powerful oil, provides you with the same relief it has for many others.

products.name: Rainbow Sherbert
products.desc: Rainbow Sherbet is an evenly-balanced hybrid marijuana strain made by crossing Champagne with Blackberry. Rainbow Sherbet is a notably tasty strain with hints of sugar and fruit. Smoking Rainbow Sherbet will have you feeling chilled out but focused enough to do something creative or inspiring. Smoking Rainbow Sherbet in large amounts will change this effect and turn your experience into a heavy-hitting euphoria. Medical marijuana patients choose Rainbow Sherbet for its pain relieving qualities.

products.name: Sherb Cream Pie
products.desc: Sherb Cream Pie is a weed strain. Yet another delicious dessert strain, Sherb Cream Pie is made from Ice Cream Cake x Sherb Bx1, which is short for Sherbert 'backcrossed' one time. Backcrossing means breeding a strain back onto itself to hopefully get more of the desirable traits. Sherm Cream Pie should be a potent indica hybrid that yields frosty, purple dapples, and popular 'candy-gas' smells. Nurseries say Sherm Cream Pie finishes flowering in the standard 9 weeks. It stretches a relatively high amount during flowering.

products.name: Zashimi
products.desc: Zashimi is a cannabis strain often made of the parents The Original Z x Mochi Gelato. Zashimi should have tropical candy taffy and creamy berry smell and taste, and a mostly green hue. Zashimi is a feature of the LA exotic cannabis scene, and consequently it subject to higher than average counterfeiting. According to credible reports Zashimi comes from a collaboration between the brand Laughing Gas, and Zeki Genetics. At its core, it's yet another Z x Sherbert cross—which has been a fruitful avenue for many a breeder and brand. Both strains have excellent, popular, appetizing syrupy-sweet tastes and versatile indica hybrid effects.

products.name: O-Dog

Opt for a joint for maximum flavor, featuring a white ash tip and a resin ring that leaves you starstruck. If you're aiming beyond being stoned, choose a blunt or wood.

GELATTI x BLACK DIAMOND X

35% THC

Umami Butter is a euphoric Indica-dominant cross of Gelatti and our very own Black Diamond X expressing a savory and creamy terpene profile. This strain displays violet and fuchsia tones interwoven between amber stigmas that sit beneath a dense sea of sticky, resinous trichomes. The Japanese word “Umami,” which translates to “essence of deliciousness,” is experienced with each flavor-packed hit of this strain, and its nose is just as rich and complex with slightly sweet and tangy undertones balancing out the bolder notes of its profile. With each smooth and flavorful exhale, the body and mind are settled further into a sweet trance that will leave you feeling deeply relaxed and at ease. This strain’s sedating qualities are sure to pack a punch, making it an excellent choice for decompression, physical recovery, or an end-of-day treat.

products.name: Durban Poison
products.desc:
OCAL ORGANIC

Durban Poison is thought to originate from South African landrace sativa seeds that were brought to the US by Ed Rosenthal in the late 1970’s. Rosenthal selectively bred these new seeds and shared his selections with fellow cultivator, Mel Frank. Frank then bred these landrace seeds creating the phenotype of Durban Poison that we know today. We have hunted through old seeds to find a phenotype closely resembling the classic Durban Poison that boasts an extremely energetic high that is perfect for daytime activities. This cultivar has dense green resinous flowers that produce a uniquely pungent skunk citrus funk aroma. Much like our other cultivars, this one tastes just like how it smells.

products.name: Grandmas Blue Cookies
products.desc: Bred by Humboldt’s Redwood Roots Family, Grandma Blue Cookies was created by crossing an unknown Kush with GSC. This indica-dominant hybrid smells like fresh cookies with sweet citrus undertones, while the flavor offers a smooth, earthy sweetness with sharp chocolate notes. The high is heavy and slow, making it a perfect strain for relaxing your mind after a long day of work.

products.name: Jack The Ripper
products.desc:
OCAL ORGANIC

Jack the Ripper seeds were bred by the infamous Sub Cool from TGA genetics and pheno hunted in house by No Till Kings. The aroma of Jack the Ripper slaps you in the face with an original lemon pine flavor that sparks nostalgia. Sticky bright green buds filled with orange hairs, this strain is truly a classic brought back to life. Jack the Ripper is a sativa dominant hybrid crossed between Cinderella 99 and Spacequeen, making it a perfect daytime strain to get out and conquer the day.

products.name: Jolly Rancherz
products.desc:
Indoor Exotic Smalls Flower Ounce - Jolly Rancherz
is a sativa-dominant hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Very Cherry and Notorious THC.
Candyland, Is a sativa marijuana strain bred from Granddaddy Purple and Bay Platinum Cookies.Bred by Humbolt Seed Company, Jelly Rancher features flavors like berry, strawberry, and citrus. The dominant terpene of this strain is caryophyllene.

products.name: Lazer Fuel
products.desc:
OCAL ORGANIC

Lazer Fuel is a cross between Gary Payton x Falcon-9 (Reverse). This heavy Indica dominant strain is mostly purple with slight hues of green and orange hairs. This strain has a powerful fuel aroma and tastes like licorice candy dipped in race gas. Trichomes cover this beautiful looking flower making it stand out amongst others. The high octane smelling flowers boost a heavy full body experience that is perfect for sleep or relaxing with some friends after a long day.

products.name: Super Boof

It has the same chunky, deep green and purple-dappled buds as its parents that look wet with silver calyxes. The effects of Super Boof are relaxing and giggly. Reviewers on Leafly say this strain makes them feel euphoric, creative and focused. Medical marijuana patients say they buy Super Boof

products.name: White Widow

OCAL ORGANIC

White Widow is a Brazilian land race sativa crossed with a south Indian indica that gained massive popularity in the 1990's. The #11 was selected due to its fruity chem aroma and phenomenal flavor. The dense green bud structure is occasionally layered with purple hues. This is a perfect strain for day time activities that won't get you too tried, yet still gives you a heavy head high.

data.desc: Time Machine is premium hydroponic flower grown in our state-of-the-art Dutch greenhouses on California’s central coast. 100% sun-grown, single source smalls, known to be the biggest smalls in the galaxy. No shake, no trim, no stems and a variety of strains with more to come!

products.name: Cereal Milk
products.desc: Like the milk that's left at the bottom after finishing a bowl of cereal, these buds will keep you coming back for more. Kick back and catch up on your to-do list or sit back and watch your favorite shows. Keep the giggles going, and the love flowing with this treat.

products.name: GMO
products.desc: Buckle up, space cadets, and prepare for liftoff with GMO, the indica strain that will take you on a journey to the stars. This potent strain is known for its unique genetic heritage and powerful effects, making it the perfect way to explore the cosmos. With a THC content of 20-25%, GMO will surely leave you feeling euphoric and energized. The Chemdawg and Tres Dawg genetics in this strain give it a pungent, diesel-like aroma, while the Afghani landrace strain adds a hint of sweetness and earthiness. The flavor is similarly pungent and diesel-like, making it a popular choice for those who prefer more potent and earthy flavors. The effects of GMO are often described as intense and well-rounded, offering a potent head high paired with a relaxing and calming body high. Many users feel like they're on a spaceship blasting through the stars, with a boost of creativity and a clear head. The strain is also known for its long-lasting effects, lasting several hours after use.

products.desc: When looking for something to take the edge off and have a nice relaxing day, the 3.5g Kush Mintz from Time Machine will do the trick. Kush Mints is a hybrid marijuana strain made by crossing Animal Mints with Bubba Kush. Kush MInts has a flavor profile consisting of coffee, woody and sweet. While its aroma is that of mint, earth, herbal, spicy, and woody. Kush Mints provides effects that are uplifting and happy. The effect will give you a solid cerebral & body high along with feelings of relaxation and hunger. Kush Mints is ideal for pain, depression, fatigue, and nausea. Pick some up and be ready for a day of relaxation and joy.

Its overall flavor profile smacks of GMO’s zesty garlic and finishes with Papaya’s terpy notes. A great smoke for relaxing after work or on a lazy day off, the effects are powerful and prolonged.

Heirbloom is grown and cultivated by the team at Cannabiotix and is focused on producing classic cannabis varieties or "heirloom" strains at top level quality. An "heirloom" is defined as: something of special value handed down from one generation to another. Here at CBX, cannabis has always been very near and dear to our hearts and we believe having a passion for the plant means everything for the user experience. Flower grown to its peak, extracted freshly, and processed into an incredibly tasty live resin for your enjoyment. It is our sincere hope that you will revel in these nostalgic phenos and pass it along to the next generation.
-------------------------

products.name: Cherry Pie
products.desc:
Cherry Pie is a clone-only strain that is believed to be an alternate phenotype originating from the breeding round that produced the infamous Girl Scout Cookies. Dating back to the mid 2000s in the Bay Area, this sweet scented bud reeks of fruity pie and is visually beautiful with darker purple hues. Notorious for being an extremely oily and resinous flower, this Indica provides a “heavy-eyed” couch lock high, making it perfect for chilling and relaxing at the end of a long day.

PCK : 10/17/24

products.name: Master Kush
products.desc: Bred in 2014 by Bay Area grower and breeder, Mario Sherbinskis, in collaboration with Jigga from the Cookie Fam, the seeds for Sunset Sherbert aka "Sherbert" eventually lead to the birth of Gelato and an explosion of the "exotics" category we see today. This mother of "Zaaa" cultivar is Known for its fruity flavor and sweet, tangy notes, this candy tasting smoke delivers an incredible dessert-like profile that matches its name. Super dense with a lighter violet hue, these stunning buds smack on multiple levels. Effects are known to be uplifting and mood enhancing while also providing blissful, full body relaxation.

products.name: Watermelon
products.desc:
An old-school mystery strain, the Watermelon is said to hail from the Vermont/Massachusetts border - originally grown outdoors and bred using open pollination techniques right next to a garden of wild blackberries, strawberries and grapes which are thought to have influenced this strains unique terpene profile. The distinct watermelon flavor with undertones of berries and hashish is undeniable. Known for providing soothing effects and ideal for those suffering with anxiety or depression, this medicinal cultivar is truly one of a kind.

PCK 10/23/24

data.name: Light Dep
data.desc: 8 Bit Buds Light Dep Half Ounce Flower offers premium, greenhouse-grown cannabis cultivated using light deprivation techniques. This method ensures dense, resin-rich buds with enhanced terpene profiles and potent effects. Each 14-gram (half-ounce) package delivers top-tier quality, making it ideal for both seasoned enthusiasts and newcomers seeking a flavorful and satisfying experience.

products.name: Alien Cookies
products.desc: A stellar fusion of sweet vanilla and funky earth, Alien Cookies takes you on a smooth ride to total relaxation with a clear-headed twist. Grown as top-tier AAA light dep flower, it delivers premium quality for elevating your everyday sesh.

products.name: SFV OG
products.desc: Bright, bold, and irresistibly smooth—this flavorful hybrid blends zesty citrus with creamy cherry for a taste that hits just right. Expect a deeply relaxing body high paired with uplifting, giggly vibes. Grown from premium small-batch indoor flower, every puff is a potent, terp-rich experience you’ll want to come back to.

data.name: Living Soil Flower
data.desc:
No Till Living Soil requires an immense amount of knowledge of soil biology and microbiology. It is a very mathematical and precise way of growing when doing it commercially.
Through extensive soil testing with third party labs, No Till Kings is able to solve complex mathematical equations to understand exactly what their soil needs cycle after cycle.
They have now used the same body of soil since they started their journey years ago and it keeps getting better!
-----------------------------------

products.name: Black Patronus
products.desc: This heavy hitting indica dominant strain is a cross between RS-11 x Falcon-9 (Reverse). Bred by Exotic Genetix, this flower has beautiful dark purple hues that almost look black, hence the name. These medium sized buds are rich in flavor with tasting notes of chocolate and butterscotch making your mouth water. The smell of this exotic flavor closely resembles a taffy like chocolate, making it a must for chocolate lovers. This strain is best suited for afternoons and evenings as it produces a euphoric full body high.

products.name: Durban Poison
products.desc: Durban Poison is thought to originate from South African landrace sativa seeds that were brought to the US by Ed Rosenthal in the late 1970’s. Rosenthal selectively bred these new seeds and shared his selections with fellow cultivator, Mel Frank. Frank then bred these landrace seeds creating the phenotype of Durban Poison that we know today. We have hunted through old seeds to find a phenotype closely resembling the classic Durban Poison that boasts an extremely energetic high that is perfect for daytime activities. This cultivar has dense green resinous flowers that produce a uniquely pungent skunk citrus funk aroma. Much like our other cultivars, this one tastes just like how it smells.

products.name: Glue
products.desc: Glue, also known as GG4, or Original Glue, was bred by GG strains. The name came about due to the intensely resinous trichomes that stuck to everything when handling the flower much like a strong glue. Glue is crossed between Chem’s Sister, Sour Dubb and Chocolate Diesel. The flower gives off intense musky gas and chocolate notes like you’re biting into your favorite chocolate bar while pumping 91 octane gas. A relaxing full body, couch locked feeling immediately hits your body when enjoying this cultivar. This heavy indica dominant strain is for the more experienced smoker, even though test results can be low. Glue’s buds are medium sized with beautiful shimmering silver and light green colors.

products.name: Jack The Ripper
products.desc: Jack the Ripper seeds were bred by the infamous Sub Cool from TGA genetics and pheno hunted in house by No Till Kings. The aroma of Jack the Ripper slaps you in the face with an original lemon pine flavor that sparks nostalgia. Sticky bright green buds filled with orange hairs, this strain is truly a classic brought back to life. Jack the Ripper is a sativa dominant hybrid crossed between Cinderella 99 and Spacequeen, making it a perfect daytime strain to get out and conquer the day.

products.name: Larry Strawberry
products.desc: Larry Strawberry is bred by Jungle Boys and is a cross of Mike Larry and Strawberry Shortcake. This cultivar is an indica dominant hybrid that has a euphoric yet calming high that's perfect for day and night. This cultivar displays aromas of strawberry shortbread cookies mixed with sweet cream. Beautifully tight sticky buds with both green and purple, make this strain shine!

products.name: Lazer Fuel
products.desc: Lazer Fuel is a cross between Gary Payton x Falcon-9 (Reverse). This heavy Indica dominant strain is mostly purple with slight hues of green and orange hairs. This strain has a powerful fuel aroma and tastes like licorice candy dipped in race gas. Trichomes cover this beautiful looking flower making it stand out amongst others. The high octane smelling flowers boasts a heavy full body experience that is perfect for sleeping or relaxing with some friends after a long day.

products.name: Lemon Banana Sherb
products.desc: This perfectly balanced 50/50 hybrid is ideal for either daytime activities or evening gatherings. Strong scents of freshly ground lemon zest infiltrate your nose when grinding this beautiful flower. Bred by Crockett Family Farms, this is a cross between Lemon Skunk and Banana Sherbert. Lemon Banana Sherbert tastes like a sweet candy lemonade without the tart. Leaving you with a medium to heavy relaxing high, this hybrid strain is truly a match made in heaven.

products.name: Mimosa
products.desc: Mimosa seeds were bred by Symbiotic Genetics and pheno hunted in house by No Till Kings. Mimosa is a cross between Clementine and Purple Punch F2. This sativa dominant hybrid smells like orange citrus candy dipped in chocolate. The bud structure is dense, with purple and orange hues coated with resinous trichomes. Mimosa tastes just how it smells, offering a unique uplifting experience that is suited for both during the day and night.

products.name: Neon Sunshine
products.desc: This heavy leaning indica strain is crossed between a Zkittlez mother and Falcon-9 (Reverse). Bred by Exotic Genetix, this flower has intense orange citrus aromas mixed with a light octane fuel. Neon Sunshine has beautiful inner purple calyxes and green hues. While exhaling the smoke, you will notice a gassy orange citrus mixture that tantalizes your taste buds. A good relaxing full bodied high accompanied with heavy eyes and an increased appetite is what some may feel when enjoying this amazing flower.

products.name: Plasma Gas
products.desc: This extraordinary vibrant flower is a show stopper. The indica dominant strain boasts deep purples and vigorous greens that shimmer brilliantly. Plasma Gas is a cross between KushCo OG x Falcon-9 (Reverse). Bred by Exotic Genetix, this strain is sure to leave you feeling a heavy full bodied high that is perfect in the evening. An abundance of smooth smoke and earthy gas mixed with genuine leather coat your taste buds while enjoying this cultivar. Musky earth aromas are predominant, although hints of sweet floral scents can be found when first cracking the jar. Plasma Gas is a strain that will remind you of a warm crackling campfire surrounded by friends.

products.name: SFV x Animal Mints
products.desc: This is an SFV dominant cross, very similar to a classic SFV giving off aromas of liquid fuel and pine. The bud has a beautiful green dense structure that is coated in trichomes. Best suited after a long day, this heavy hitting indica strain has a full body high that will keep you feeling relaxed and happy.

products.name: White Widow #11
products.desc: White Widow is a Brazilian land race sativa crossed with a south Indian indica that gained massive popularity in the 1990's. The #11 was selected due to its fruity chem aroma and phenomenal flavor. The dense green bud structure is occasionally layered with purple hues. This is a perfect strain for day time activities that won't get you too tried, yet still gives you a heavy head high.

data.name: Misfits Flower
data.desc:
Embrace your uniqueness and make contact with AlienLabs Misfit Flower. If you've ever been called a Misfit, eccentric, or just plain weird, you'll feel right at home with this out-of-this-world cannabis experience.
With AlienLabs Flower, perfection is the mission. Each batch is carefully graded, taking into account its smell, color, structure, trim, and moisture content. Expert eyes from the AlienLabs team meticulously evaluate every single batch, ensuring that only the best of the best make their way into the stellar AlienLabs jar.
But here's the twist— not even Aliens get it perfect every time. The unpredictable beauty of the cannabis plant means that not every yield receives a perfect score. That's where Misfits come in.
Misfits are the rebels—the outstanding cannabis that might not be flawless but is still outer-wordly by any standard. Inspired by the pursuit of excellence, AlienLabs offers you Misfits, a chance to enjoy premium cannabis at an unbeatable value.

data.name: Moon Rocks
data.desc:
Moon Rocks done right...!

Forget everything you thought you knew about Moon Rocks — CE’s Moon Rocks are on a whole new level. Crafted with premium flower, drenched in cured resin, and finished with a coat of 90u hash... these heavy hitters deliver an unmatched, supremely dank experience. Smooth, potent, and absolutely dripping in quality, ready to launch you into another dimension.

Buckle up and blast off with CE’s next-level Moon Rocks — you’ve never flown this high before... 🚀

products.name: Banana Alien Candy
products.desc: Experience the irresistible charm of Alien Banana Candy — a mouthwatering hybrid that delivers sweet satisfaction with a powerful, uplifting high. Bursting with the sugary flavor of ripe banana candies and layered with hints of juicy berries and a touch of earthy nuttiness, this strain is pure bliss from the first hit. Perfect for hybrid lovers seeking a bright, euphoric buzz and a flavor that’s out of this world, Alien Banana Candy is your new go-to for unforgettable sessions.

products.name: Boysenberry Boogie
products.desc: Get ready to groove with Boysenberry Boogie — a potent, flavor-packed strain that’s as therapeutic as it is delicious. Enjoy a smooth, rich berry taste, highlighted by hints of juicy blueberries and zesty citrus. This powerhouse delivers a dank, woody aroma that melts away anxiety, relieves pain and muscle spasms, and tackles appetite issues with ease. Its musky, earthy scent uplifts your spirits, eases stress, and infuses your mood with a burst of euphoric energy. Whether you need a creative spark or a mood boost, Boysenberry Boogie will have you feeling vibrant, inspired, and ready to take on the world.

products.name: Cosmic Fruit Punch
products.desc: Blast off with Cosmic Fruit Punch — the ultimate hybrid experience that’s truly out of this world! This stellar strain delivers a deep, all-over body buzz perfectly balanced with a smooth, mellow head high. Whether you need a daytime lift or a relaxing way to unwind after work, Cosmic Punch hits the sweet spot between energizing and soothing. Get ready to elevate your mood, relax your body, and enjoy cosmic vibes any time of day.

products.name: Galactic Blue Razz
products.desc: Reach for the stars with Galactic Blue Razz — the ultimate treat for true indica lovers. Break apart these glittering nugs and unleash an irresistible burst of skunky floral notes, juicy blueberries, and a tangy hint of sour raspberries. With flavor and potency this bold, Galactic Blue Razz is your ticket to deep relaxation and out-of-this-world bliss.

products.name: Mango Sunrise
products.desc: Wake up your senses with Mango Sunrise — a rare, exotic hybrid bursting with tropical flavor and vibrant aroma. Born from the legendary Mango and Sunrise Sherbet strains, this delicious powerhouse delivers waves of juicy sweetness with every hit. Perfect for seasoned cannabis lovers, Mango Sunrise offers a deeply relaxing, blissful high that melts away stress and sparks your appetite. Whether you're chasing pure chill vibes or looking for a tropical escape, Mango Sunrise will leave you floating in paradise.

products.name: Rainbow Runtz
products.desc: Rainbow Runtz shines bright with a terpene profile dominated by limonene, myrcene, and caryophyllene, delivering an aroma that’s as zesty as it is grounding. This balanced hybrid blends citrusy notes with a hint of earthiness, finishing with a peppery kick for extra flair. With flavors as layered as its genetics—Rainbow Chip x Runtz—this flower is your go-to smoke for a relaxed headspace or a creative spark. Chase this rainbow and find your flavor-packed gold.

A great smoke for those with jitters on their big day, this Wedding Cake is known to soothe and relax frayed nerves.

data.name: Premium CUREFlower
data.desc: West Coast Cure’s Premium Flowers are cultivated in boutique batches from California’s best cultivators. Grown in mixed light, greenhouse, farm-grown, and sun-grown environments, these terpene-rich flowers contain a minimum of 25% THC. Available in 3.5g, 14g, and 28g and sold in resealable mylar packages, this product line provides high-quality savings for the daily connoisseur and ballers on a budget.

products.name: Apple Fritter
products.desc: Who’s ready to get “baked” with WCC’s Apple Fritter Premium Flower? This Indica-forward Hybrid, crafted by Lumpy’s Flowers, is a heavyweight in both aroma and effects. The buds are chunky, knuckled, and dripping with frosty trichomes, delivering a sweet and earthy scent that feels like a fresh batch of homemade goodness. Perfect for those vibe-shift moments, Apple Fritter’s soothing effects transport you to a peaceful place.

products.name: Cookies Sherbet
products.desc: Cookie OG Premium Flower is a delicious Hybrid by-product of two distinguished West Coast strains. Just as the name implies, it represents the mashup of NorCal’s Cookie gene pool and a SoCal OG Kush. A 50-50 hybrid strain with a complex flavor profile, these genetics produce a distinct petrol, earth, and nutty flavor profile. Blessed with pungent terpenes and a strong herbal nose, Cookie OG will not disappoint!

products.name: Durban Poison
products.desc: Durban Poison Premium Flower offers that refined Sativa kick, loaded with petrol zest and an earthy, spicy nose…it’s all about the uplift. This legendary strain rocks tight, conical buds that throw off an energetic aroma of Terpinolene, Ocimene, Myrcene, and a touch of anethole. A go-to smoke for sparking up a breezy headspace, Durban Poison unleashes untapped creativity with a relaxing vibe.

products.name: Forbidden Runtz
products.desc: Forbidden Runtz Premium Flower is, as some might surmise, a Hybrid cross of Forbidden Fruit x Runtz. An amazing phenotype selected for its inspired aroma and heady flavor, its tangy zest smacks of sweet Limonene and Linalool with just the right amount of petrol. A chill smoke with a creative vibe, its effects provide a balanced headspace of relaxed inspiration.

products.name: Frozen Cherries

products.name: Garapples
products.desc: Garapples Premium Flower is where the game gets real, bringing that high-quality Indica vibe straight to your doorstep. Crossed with the champs, Gary Payton x Apples N Bananas, these nugs are all about that flavor slam dunk. Packed with a diesel funk zest that’s off the charts, Garapples is your three-point shot for that potent punch of taste and chill. Light it up and sink into that terpy high, where cerebral relaxation isn’t just a play—it’s the winning move.

products.name: Gelato 41
products.desc: Gelato #41 Premium Flower is the plug, packed with a squad of fire terps—Caryophyllene bringing the heat with that spicy kick, Limonene hitting fresh with a citrus twist, Humulene grounding it with some earthy vibes, and Myrcene keeping it all laid-back. This strain’s all about flavor and flow, making it the perfect pick for kicking back with your crew. Whether you’re chilling or just trying to catch a vibe, Gelato #41’s got that smooth, euphoric high that keeps it 100. It’s where luxury meets that laid-back lifestyle.

data.name: Premium Flower
data.desc:
The West Coast Cure team are nonconformists who have been loyal to cannabis since the prohibition days. For decades, they have been hunting and hand-selecting the gassiest strains while fostering relationships with cultivators and innovative wax artists. Winning the first NorCal Cannabis Cup for Concentrates in 2012 was the crowning moment for their brand’s vision.

They aren’t a new market entrant who joined the game after 2018 to make inferior products without a heart. They are West Coast Cure, the hardcore OGs who bring you crazy fire weed.

Overview
West Coast Cure’s Premium Flowers are cultivated in boutique batches from California’s best cultivators. Grown in mixed light, greenhouse, farm-grown, and sun-grown environments, these terpene-rich flowers contain a minimum of 25% THC.

products.desc: There is some dispute over the true parents of this indica-dominant award winner: Some sources claim they're F1Durb (an indica-dominant descendant of Durban Poison) and Florida OG (a little known indica). data.name: Premium Flower 3.5g
data.desc:
Hand Crafted


All aspects of our cultivation are manually controlled and truly crafted by hand. We make a point of giving each plant individualized attention to ensure that all plants are equally cared for. With our expansive genetic library, we cultivate 10-15 strains at once, which requires us to be very attentive throughout the plants entire life. Each strain is cared for differently depending on the genetics' unique characteristics of growth. Applying meticulous hands-on techniques and specially formulated recipes with the sole purpose of creating the finest and most flavorful cannabis in the world, we are able to produce products that are rightfully in their own elite level of what cannabis can and should be.

Hand Trimmed


It is extremely important to us that the flowers are never mishandled to ensure the cannabinoids and terpenes are preserved to the highest degree possible. All leaves and stems are carefully removed keeping in tact all the calyxes and pistils while never directly touching the actual flowers.

Hand Packaged


To ensure elite quality down to each and every gram, we carefully hand package all of our flowers. We believe that delicately hand-packaging flowers is the best way to truly preserve the integrity of the product.

-----------------------------------------------------------

This strain usually induces a soaring, long-lasting buzz perfect for creative escapes, but can push past the confines of a subtle buzz into the weighty “couch-lock” effects when consumed in higher doses

Plasma Gas is a strain that will remind you of a warm crackling campfire surrounded by friends.

data.name: Premium Flowers
data.desc:
Welcome to "Made," the cannabis brand created exclusively for the real culture of cannabis enthusiasts.
At "Made," we embrace the essence of cannabis in its purest form. Our journey began with a simple belief: that the true essence of cannabis lies not just in its consumption but in the connections it fosters, the memories it weaves, and the sense of community it creates. Drawing inspiration from the rich history of this ancient plant, "Made" emerges as a brand that cherishes and preserves the legacy of cannabis, crafting products that speak to the heart of true connoisseurs.
Our Slogan: "Made for Smokers": We proudly stand behind our slogan, "Made for Smokers," because we understand that our products are designed for those who truly appreciate the nuances of the cannabis experience. Whether you're a seasoned enthusiast or just beginning to explore the world of cannabis, "Made" offers a curated selection that caters to your unique preferences.

710 is obsessed with making the richest flavored, pesticide-free, organically fed, small batch, hand-trimmed cannabis on the planet. We are the OGs that hand select and hunt exotic strains from the most renowned breeders, including Landrace single original seeds that took decades to find.

Overview
 There’s a reason 710 flower is renowned industry wide – they never blind source. 710 meticulously grow their flowers in house, with wholly organic inputs, dry and cure it based on density, and trim it by hand to bring you the most opulent, flavor dense nugs on the market.

data.name: Premium Indoor Flower
data.desc:
At the forefront of cultivating elite sativa, indica, and hybrid strains, Alien Labs has redefined excellence with standout strains like Area 41 and Biskantè. As a game-changer in the California cannabis market, their innovative journey hasn't just stopped at exceptional buds.

---------------------------------------

products.name: Agent X
products.desc: Alien Labs Premium Indoor Flower 3.5G - Agent X

products.name: Area 41
products.desc:
Area 41 was bred and selected with the intention of bringing big gas back to the flavor conversation and power back to the top shelf. By lending the bag appeal of Gelato 41 to an old-school OG cut and selecting it based on the flavor of the Lemon Fuel OG, we think Area 41 checks every box.
-----
Hybrid
Lineage: Lemon Fuel Og x Gelato #41
-----
Prominent terpenes: D-Limonene, β-Myrcene, β-Caryophyllene

products.name: Atomic Apple
products.desc:
Atomic Apple is truly out of this world with its beautiful bud structure looking like a meteor coming out of orbit. Deep shades of purple look like the cosmic nebula, surrounded by tones of green hues, & small orange hairs tightly clustered. Tastes like sour apple candy with hints of fuel and vanilla cream terpenes. The high-testing cannabinoid profiles will take you to another dimension.

-----
Hybrid
Lineage: Triangle Mints x Apple Fritter
-----
Prominent terpenes: D-Limonene, β-Myrcene, β-Caryophyllene

products.name: Biskanté
products.desc:
Absolutely incredible taste and smell on this new strain from Alien Labs. Biscotti-style flavor with a pound of sweetness. We’ve crossed a lot of lemon strains and they usually always carry a very heavy lemon terp, and while this has some of the same sweetness, it’s very mild on the lemon - turning this into something pretty damn unique. The same effect can be described as a Sativa-dominant hybrid.

-----
Sativa Dominant Hybrid
Lineage: Melonade x Biscotti #6
-----
Prominent terpenes: D-Limonene, β-Caryophyllene, α-Humulene

products.name: Biskanté*
products.desc: Alien Labs Premium Indoor Flower 3.5G - Biskante - PCKG DATE: MARCH2024

products.name: BK Satellite
products.desc:
BK Satellite is a hybrid strain crossing Legend of Nigeria with Milky Way. Expect a sweet aroma with flavors of fruitiness and spice. The effects are relaxing, and full-bodied thanks to the heavy indica influence. Expertly picked at peak freshness just light up to transport yourself straight into another galaxy.

-----
Hybrid
Lineage: Legend Of Nigeria x Milky Way
-----
Prominent terpenes: β-Caryophyllene, D-Limonene, β-Myrcene

products.name: Creme De Menthe
products.desc: Alien Labs Premium Indoor Flower 3.5G - Creme De Menthe

products.name: Dark Web
products.desc:
Floral, sugary and slightly spicy with subtle vanilla high notes whose sweetness will linger in your nose even after you’ve resecured the lid. The deep purple margins are contrasted nicely by the orange of the soft bushy pistils bringing to mind a Halloween color scheme. A thick coat of twinkling trichomes make this flower look better than sour candy. These very dense and triangular nugs resemble the wrist bones of a long dead demon or those four sided dice you need for attack rolls in DnD. The flavor is creamy and berry sweet on the pull with an earthy yet smooth exhale and a slightly soapy aftertaste. A soothing and relaxing hybrid, consumption of which results in a clear headed high with a nice body-buzz. Good for movies, playing some games or just kicking back with friends. Not bad for creative work either as it will keep you focused and alert.
-----
Hybrid
Lineage:
UNKNOWN CLONE ONLY
----- Prominent terpenes:
D-Limonene
β-Caryophyllene
Linalool

products.name: Gemini
products.desc:
Gemini is a wonderfully complex new strain from the team at Alienlabs. This has a multilayered taste and smell, one is earthy, aggressive OG funk, and the other is a sweet candied grape “dust” flavor. The earthy sweetness comes through in the flavor and creates a wonderful head/body effect that is sure to get even the high-tolerance users where they want to be.

-----
Indica
Lineage: 2 Face OG x Area 41
-----
Prominent terpenes: D-Limonene, β-Myrcene, β-Caryophyllene

products.name: KryptoChronic
products.desc:
Kryptochronic ((Fruity Pebbles OG x Alien Cookies) x Jet Fuel Gelato) is a vibrant lime green with purple undertones and bright orange pistils. Tastes and smells like you put gas in your bowl of fruity pebbles instead of milk.
-----
Indica Dominant Hybrid
Lineage: (Fruity Pepples OG x Alien Cookies) x Jet Fuel Gelato
-----
Prominent terpenes: D-Limonene, β-Caryophyllene, α-Humulene

products.name: Planet Red
products.desc:
Its sweet and juicy fruit aroma with minty high notes will make your mouth water the moment you open the jar. Deep greens and bushy pistils are all unified by a thick glaze of trichomes giving the flower a silvery frosted look. In fact, these dense and sticky little pine trees look like they got caught in a snow storm. The flavor profile is pleasantly sweet and sugary on the pull, with a prominent and biting tarry exhale. This strain will untie the knots in your mind and soothe the knots in your body just like a warm bath. A balanced hybrid with highly relaxing properties, great for sore muscles or just an end of the day smoke.

Planet Red is not just a strain; it's an interstellar experience. Like the Aliens intended.
-----
Hybrid
Lineage: Red Pop x Apples & Bananas #9
-----
Prominent terpenes: β-Caryophyllene, D-Limonene, Linalool

products.name: Zangria
products.desc:
GSC x Z
The scent of this flower is otherworldly, a potent fusion that evokes distant memories of alien orchards. Its fragrance hints at luscious, unfamiliar fruits from its Zkittlez ancestry, layered with the warm, doughy undertones of its Girl Scout cookie heritage. The flower itself shimmers under the glow of starlight, its surface coated in crystalline trichomes, casting a cool, metallic grey hue. When dissected, vibrant purples and rich greens glimmer beneath the surface, as if hiding the colors of some extraterrestrial jungle. The taste is a creamy, sugary delight, reminiscent of interstellar confections, contrasted by a mellow, doughy aftertaste that lingers long after consumption. Once inhaled, it floods your system with a tranquil energy, relaxing your body and soothing your mind. Uniquely, Zangria keeps your focus sharp, making it perfect for exploration, whether you’re navigating through daily tasks, night time activities, or the vastness of space.

data.name: Premium Indoor Flower
data.desc: Our pre-packaged flower comes in a variety of premium Indica, Sativa, and Hybrid strains.  Our flower is hand-trimmed and carefully handled to maintain the integrity and quality of each flower.

products.name: 98 Reserve
products.desc: Our journey began with a single seed of the legendary Pre 98 Bubba Kush, igniting our passion for cultivating connoisseur-quality cannabis. After twenty-five years, we're returning to our roots with 98 Reserve, a tribute to our progress. This innovative Indica cross captures the timeless essence of Pre 98 Bubba Kush, elevated with the modern classic Runtz. These sugar-coated buds emit a musky, herbal aroma with pungent notes of conifer and citrus that tingle the nostrils, followed by sweet, woodsy undertones that culminate in a robust, coffee-like exhalation.

products.name: Blue Agape
products.desc: Blue Agape, an Indica cross of our Blue Lotus and White Runtz and the first strain we released through our Research & Development line, is a potent, hard-hitting strain with a memorable terpene profile. While two phenotypes of this new strain (#9 and #23) went head to head, our community favored #9, and we are excited to bring it into full production. Because of its high terpene content, this Indica offers a bold aroma, flavor profile, and unique and long-lasting high. Earthy, spicy, pine-forward notes experienced upon breaking the nugs apart are enhanced with every flavor-packed hit. Similar to its parent strains, Blue Agape offers a mellow, relaxing high that is both medicinal and enjoyable for recreational purposes.

products.name: Blue Lotus
products.desc: Blue Lotus is the second edition of our limited black box series. A cross of Blue Gelato #41 and our very own XXX OG, this strain is the selected winner out of 12 different phenotypes that all showed amazing traits. True to its OG lineage, this pungent and heavy-hitting Indica has an intense gassy aroma and terpene profile that is complemented by earthy notes and sweet undertones. This high comes on fast and strong with a heavy-headed cerebral buzz followed by deep physical relaxation and euphoria. As a true Indica, Blue Lotus offers many traits that can assist with treating pain, stress, insomnia, anxiety and nausea or loss of appetite. Whether you’re enjoying this strain recreationally or using it medicinally, it is sure to provide a bold experience for the senses and a strong, long-lasting high.

products.name: Chroma
products.desc: Gleaming with a silver sheen and stacked with trichomes, Chroma is a striking cross of our multiple award-winning Prizm and Black Diamond X — two powerhouse cultivars known for their bold terpene profiles and heavy-handed effects. This next-generation phenotype reflects its name with radiant bag appeal and a bold aromatic spectrum that opens with citrus rind and sharp pine, then deepens into notes of dark stone fruit, floral musk, and clean fuel.

products.name: French Lotus
products.desc: French Lotus is an exquisite, violet-hued cross that reflects the finest traits of our two most distinguished strains, FKAFL and Blue Lotus. A dank, earthy fragrance reminiscent of a fresh meadow after rainfall is beautifully complemented by hints of citrus, with a subtle umami undertone that intensifies upon combustion. Like the daily renewal of the lotus, shedding the impurities of its environment, this Hybrid can help alleviate stress and negativity, leaving one feeling resilient and revitalized.

products.name: Key Lime Jack
products.desc: In collaboration with Happy Dreams Genetics, Key Lime Jack is an effervescent Sativa with a bright and summery aroma. This cross of Bling Cheesecake and Jack Herrer has sweet, sharp, and slightly sour citrus notes that fill the air upon opening a jar, creating a zesty and refreshing inhale. A skunky and earthy exhale instantly uplifts the mind, relaxes the body, and boosts your mood. This cerebral buzz is bubbly, long-lasting, and offers a euphoric high while increasing focus and keeping the mind sharp and alert.

products.name: Lip Smackerz
products.desc: ipsmackerz is a mouthwatering Indica-dominant Hybrid bred by Good Greens, resulting from a cross of (LCG x Z Animal Cookies) x Good Greens Candy #4.  This strain captivates the eyes and taste buds, showcasing vibrant purple flowers, long amber hairs, and a light dusting of crystalline sugar trichomes.  An irresistible candy-like aroma is followed by subtle fruity notes that envelop the senses with a playful sweetness. In contrast, acrid undertones of gas add layers of depth to the exhale.  Lipsmackerz truly embodies its name, offering a lingering sensation that leaves you with a smile and a delightful aftertaste.

products.name: Prizm
products.desc: Prizm is a brilliant pure Indica-dominant cross of our Opal and Permanent Marker #12 strains, with shimmering spade-shaped buds that catch the eye. Upon opening the jar, the initial clean, astringent, almost chemical-like scent gives way to more pleasant notes of pine needles and citrus candy. A lovely floral medley dances on the taste-buds, leading to a sharp, lemon-diesel smoke that dazzles the senses. This spectrum of vivid flavors mirrors its sedative qualities and transforms stress, revealing the hidden beauty present in everyday life.

products.name: D-Lish
products.desc:
Zkittlez x Sweet Retreat

D-lish is the same cross as the Fun Dip but the parents are reversed. Sweet grape and warm baked dough complement a candy finish. The taste is like a grape bubble gum blended with a toaster strudel and a tart Z finish. The flavor is intense and sugary and lingers long on the palette. The D-lish is stoney and creative but neutral with an effect that is neither up or down.

products.name: Gelonade
products.desc:
Lemontree x G41

Citrus essence continues into a complex diesel like gas with subtle hints of pepper and sorbet that potentiate the brightness of the lemon. The flavor is like sweet lemonade blended with burnt rubber and has a zesty finish that rejuvenates the palette. The effect of Gelonade is uplifting and heady and known to inspire creativity.

products.name: White Taffi
products.desc:
unconfirmed genetics

Nutty and gassy with subtle notes of menthol and tropical fruit. The taste is sharp and minty with a strong hazelnut gas and notes of pineapple and guava in the background. The smoke is full bodied in character and is extra flavorful making the White Taffi a satisfying experience. The effect is quick and full strength and felt throughout the entire body.

Each seasoned breath emits piquant notes of cracked black peppercorn and lemon rind, offering hints of dried apple and floral accents that culminate into a smooth, flawless smoke

products.name: Blue Agape
products.desc: Blue Agape, an Indica cross of our Blue Lotus and White Runtz and the first strain we released through our Research & Development line, is a potent, hard-hitting strain with a memorable terpene profile. While two phenotypes of this new strain (#9 and #23) went head to head, our community favored #9, and we are excited to bring it into full production. Because of its high terpene content, this Indica offers a bold aroma, flavor profile, and unique and long-lasting high. Earthy, spicy, pine-forward notes experienced upon breaking the nugs apart are enhanced with every flavor-packed hit. Similar to its parent strains, Blue Agape offers a mellow, relaxing high that is both medicinal and enjoyable for recreational purposes.

products.name: French Lotus
products.desc: French Lotus is an exquisite, violet-hued cross that reflects the finest traits of our two most distinguished strains, FKAFL and Blue Lotus. A dank, earthy fragrance reminiscent of a fresh meadow after rainfall is beautifully complemented by hints of citrus, with a subtle umami undertone that intensifies upon combustion. Like the daily renewal of the lotus, shedding the impurities of its environment, this Hybrid can help alleviate stress and negativity, leaving one feeling resilient and revitalized.

products.name: Panta Rhei
products.desc: Panta Rhei is a dynamic cross of our Blue Agape #9 and Oro, with midnight purple buds, fiery orange hairs, and glimmering trichomes resembling the brink of twilight. This strain's evolution in flavor and aroma embodies the ancient Greek philosophy "everything flows," offering a journey of sensory expansion that shifts from sweet, gentle earth tones into a resonant blend of evergreen, citrus fruit, and gas. This transformative Indica is an ode to the beauty of change and encourages one to find the balance between stillness and movement.

products.name: Prizm x Apples & Diamonds
products.desc: Maven's Research and Development half-ounce Maven Minis showcase exclusive micro-batches of unique phenotypes currently under evaluation, like Prizm x Apples & Diamonds. By testing and providing feedback, you can help shape the industry and influence the future of Maven cannabis. As we continue to push the boundaries of what's possible, we value your input and look forward to your thoughts on these emerging strains. Your feedback is crucial in sculpting the future of Maven cannabis. Scan the QR code to give feedback & have a chance to win Maven gear!

products.name: Shangri-La
products.desc: Behold the timeless Shangri-la. This harmonious fusion of Opal and Paradiso #11 displays mountainous buds in captivating tones of lush forest green and royal violet, set against a backdrop of pure white snow that blankets their majestic peaks, resembling a scene of a mystical utopia. Revel in a sensory voyage of unrivaled bliss with a blend of delicate floral aromas and luscious fruit enhanced by whispers of earthiness and diesel while a symphony of tart, candied notes linger on the palate. This enchanting Indica-dominant Hybrid is a treasure of a strain that rivals heaven on earth for those seeking peace and tranquility.

Silver Iris OG is an exceptional Indica-dominant Hybrid that embodies the regal lineage of our Maven OG and Zkittlez, with elegant sage green buds and prominent amber hairs that contrast a fine, pearly coating of trichomes. The rich fragrance of timeless, earthy OG mingles with hints of floral citrus that blossom into a lively arrangement when exhaled, leaving a delicate essence of fruit on the tongue. Like a flower that thrives under tender care, this strain cultivates a deep sense of mindfulness and contentment, grounding one in body, mind, and soul.

data.name: Premium Smalls
data.desc:
Hand Crafted


All aspects of our cultivation are manually controlled and truly crafted by hand. We make a point of giving each plant individualized attention to ensure that all plants are equally cared for. With our expansive genetic library, we cultivate 10-15 strains at once, which requires us to be very attentive throughout the plants entire life. Each strain is cared for differently depending on the genetics' unique characteristics of growth. Applying meticulous hands-on techniques and specially formulated recipes with the sole purpose of creating the finest and most flavorful cannabis in the world, we are able to produce products that are rightfully in their own elite level of what cannabis can and should be.

Hand Trimmed


It is extremely important to us that the flowers are never mishandled to ensure the cannabinoids and terpenes are preserved to the highest degree possible. All leaves and stems are carefully removed keeping in tact all the calyxes and pistils while never directly touching the actual flowers.

Hand Packaged


To ensure elite quality down to each and every gram, we carefully hand package all of our flowers. We believe that delicately hand-packaging flowers is the best way to truly preserve the integrity of the product.

data.name: Small Batch Craft Cannabis
data.desc:
Craft cannabis is grown in small batches of plants grown with direct care from the master grower.
With extra care and attention paid to each plant, the grower can maximize the quality of the strain.
Craft cannabis is more concerned with local taste than national appeal. It is far from a new concept.
Small batch growing is also part of the craft. This means there is not a lot of inventory.
Good strains will go fast and great strains go faster! Once it’s gone, that strain may not return right away!
Where in a commercial grow, they may have room where they keep mother plants alive for years, this is not the case for most craft cannabis grows.
For them, holding on to a strain means they do not have room for anything new.

The high is the type to creep up on you, before you know it you’ll be in cloud 9 almost on meditation mode, but yet with enough clarity to get through your day.

data.name: Wonderbrett Premium Indoor Flower 3.5g
data.desc:
In the summer of 1997, Brett was gifted the original OG Kush, a legendary West Coast strain of mythic proportions, and everything changed. Before he knew it, Brett was among the elite growers in the Los Angeles scene. When smokers wanted the best weed, they simply had to ask “You got that Brett?” By ‘99, Brett was providing cannabis to some of the biggest artists in the music industry. Dr. Dre’s influential album, 2001, was recorded with Snoop Dogg, Eminem, Xzibit and Brett’s OG Kush in the studio.

In 2014, Brett and his business partner Cam, decided it to was time to bring their legendary strains to the masses. Brett united his reliability, credibility and genetics knowledge with Cam’s engineering and electrical ingenuity and created Wonderbrett. The cannabis community hasn’t been the same since.

products.name: 11 ROSES
products.desc:
Jeeter Baby Cannon Live Resin Infused Pre-Roll (1.3g)- Bango
Bango is an Indica strain with a rich terpene profile and tropical flavors worth sharing. This Indica is a combination of White Fire Alien OG and Mango Kush, exhibiting subtle hints of each on the nose and palate. With sweet, fruity flavors of mango, banana, and pine, and an aroma with sweet floral notes and citrus peel, Bango offers an enchanting bouquet that will linger in the air. Bango’s effects are equal parts cerebral and stimulating and will get you talking. This strain is preferred for mood elevation, appetite stimulation, and nullifying depression.

products.name: Aloha
products.desc:
Jeeter Baby Cannon Live Resin Infused Pre-Roll (1.3g)- Aloha
Aloha is a sativa strain that leaves users with an upbeat, energetic buzz and may also be helpful in treating pain such as migraines. Aloha’s flowers will be large and fluffy, with plenty of room for white wispy hairs and sparkling crystals. The aroma of this strain is that of grass and citrus for a fresh experience that may have you thinking of your next island getaway. Its sativa effects can be a little much for some users, so those who are looking for less mental stimulation should be warned.

data.name: BackPack Boyz Hash Hole
data.desc: Backpack Boyz are natives of the Bay Area, growing great cannabis while maintaining a flashy image filled with champagne bottles, dollar bills, and cool cars. The Bay Area has its share when it comes to exotic cannabis, flavors, and eye-popping packaging. Backpack Boyz is a California-based marijuana brand that brings a ton of premium strains while also giving you a wide choice of flavors.

products.name: Bubblegum Gelato
products.desc:
Product Overview
Backpack Boyz Hash Hole - Bubblegum Gelato
Bubblegum Gelato is a combination of Gelato #45 and Indiana Bubblegum strains. The strain is an Indica dominated strainwith a fruity dessert-like aroma and taste that are truly pleasing to the senses–bright, earthy, and sweet. This strain gives tingles to your taste buds as you drift to the relaxation that you deserve. It has a bubble gum scent which becomes a floral/earthy smell after continuous sniffing. As you inhale, there is that initial earthy sweetness that makes each draw more and more pleasing. As you exhale, you get a deep woody/nutty note, as well as a tinge of sharpie scent-like flavor.

products.name: COCO Lato
products.desc:
Product Overview
Backpack Boyz Hash Hole - White Cherry Gelato
White Cherry Gelato crosses Sunset Sherbert with Thin Mint Girl Scout Cookies. It has a sweet flavor profile that mixes tart cherries and refreshing citrus together to create a smooth, fruity taste that’s unlike other flavors on the market. It has a unique aroma with notes of sweet berries and cherries. This high will have you feeling giggly and completely at ease with the world around you. You’ll feel an influx of cerebral creativity, giving you limitless artistic vision as your mind soars to new heights. The White Cherry Gelato high settles in almost as soon as you exhale, hitting your mind first with a lifted effect before working its way throughout your entire body.

data.name: Cannon Live Rosin
data.desc:
Introducing a new Cannon to the arsenal. Jeeter Solventless Cannons combine the artisanal live rosin experience with top-quality flower, meticulously chosen to deliver a nuanced, connoisseur smoking experience.

Live Rosin is a natural solventless cannabis concentrate derived from pressing ice-water hash. This process yields a concentrate that offers perhaps the truest flavor experience of cannabis, as it gently extracts aromatic compounds without degradation.

Unlike traditional solvent extraction methods, rosin extraction uses minimal heat and pressure to extract resin directly from trichome glands, without heavy machinery or additional solvents. Since no solvents are used, live rosin does not require purging and can be consumed fresh from the press. This minimal post-processing, combined with a gentle extraction process, preserves the unique terpene profile of each strain almost perfectly, making high-quality live rosin one of the most sought-after concentrates available today.

products.name: Blue Flame OG
products.desc: This mutant runt of our award-winning Thicc Mint Cookies crossed with our Private Reserve OG is one of the most unique flavors of the CBX Genetic Library, spawning cult classics such as our award-winning Kush Mountains and Casino Kush. A potent smoke for the experienced smoker, this true pressure OG will have you wiping the sweat from your forehead after just a couple hits and a heavy-headed high that will have your eyes feeling extra droopy as you take a soothing, sedating, and tranquil journey through the history of true old school California Kush. Sticky and resinous with unique hints of aquamarine coloring, these dense glistening gems of pure fire have very little leaf for maximum roll-up potential and can help with insomnia, anxiety, and chronic pain.

products.name: Jet Lag OG
products.desc: Descending from the godparents of gas, Kush Mountains and Red Eye OG, this pheno is a fuel forward cut with strong Indica attributes. Reeking like old school dank, the beautiful buds on this one shimmer with tight crystals, representing both parents perfectly when it comes to both structure and aroma. Rolling up reveals even deeper layers of that classic OG profile, bringing forth a clear yet couch-lock effect, ideal for late night sessions or help knocking out after a long journey. This smooth, tasty kush smoke will have you feeling chill AMF, and may lead to periods of relaxing, sedating, and tranquil states of mind.

products.name: L'Orange
products.desc: This lemony orange Cannabiotix creation is a cross between the award winning Hybrid, Orange Crush and our uplifting Lemonburst. This unique citrus terpy flower takes her time to mature, but is well worth it, as it’s known: all good things take time. The buds possess extremely sticky resinous trichomes that cling to your fingertips when broken down and fill the room with a nostalgic aroma reminiscent of sliced oranges served up at halftime of your childhood youth soccer game. Known for having a cerebral “happy” high, this strain provides a euphoric buzz that is great for relieving anxiety and depression.

products.name: Blue Dream x Banana Breath
products.desc:
THC: 35%
TERPENES: 1.9%
INSIDE: Blue Dream x Banana OG
TASTE: Sweet, Fruity, Earthy
FEELING: Relaxed, Euphoric
FARM: Mattole Valley Sungrown, East Mill Creek Farms
PLACE GROWN: Humboldt, CA
CULTIVATION STYLE: Outdoor, Sungrown

Made with Blue Dream flower cultivated by Mattole Valley Sungrown and Banana OG hash cultivated by East Mill Creek Farns.
Cultivated by Mattole Valley Sungrown - Located in the heart of the Mattole Valley in Humboldt. A Family-owned and operated farm growing premium cannabis in full sun, native soils, and rainwater.
Blue Dream is a popular and well-balanced hybrid strain known for its delightful blend of flavors and aromas. With a sweet, berry-like taste reminiscent of blueberries and hints of vanilla, it offers a smooth and enjoyable smoking experience. The aroma is equally inviting, featuring a fragrant mix of ripe fruit and earthy undertones, often accompanied by subtle notes of pine and spice.
East Mill Creek showcases a 10,000 square foot outdoor native soil cannabis farm located 5 miles inland on the north-end of the Lost Coast. East Mill Creek is built on an uplifted ocean terrace with a deep layer of topsoil blown in by the wind over time, making it an ideal texture and environment for cannabis roots to grow unencumbered.
Banana OG blends OG Kush and Banana strains creating an indica-dominate combination. It boasts a sweet banana-like aroma with earthly undertones. This combo is prized for its potent effects, primarily leaving users feeling relaxed, sleepy, and hungry. Perfect for evening use as it's laid-back high makes seeking a deep relaxation easy.

products.name: Blue Zkittles
products.desc:
2.5g 5 pack of Blue Zkittles (.5g each) mini cone prerolls. 

Blue Zkittlez, also known as "Blue Skittles" and "Blue Zkittles," is an indica marijuana strain made by crossing Blue Diamond with Zkittlez. This odoriferous flower offers a terpene profile of tart citrus, sweet earth, and wildflowers. The effects of Blue Zkittlez are mellow and moderately sedating, stimulating appetite while weighing heavy on the limbs. This strain offers a combination of strong physical effects and uplifting mental high which make it a perfect end-of-the-day strain and a nice match for folks contending with stress, restlessness, and pain.

products.name: Lemon Cherry Gelato
products.desc: 2.5g 5 pack of Lemon Cherry Gelato (.5g each) mini cone prerolls. Lemon Cherry Gelato is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Sunset Sherbet and Girl Scout Cookies. Lemon Cherry Gelato effects include tingly, relaxed, and euphoric. Medical marijuana patients often choose Lemon Cherry Gelato when dealing with symptoms associated with anxiety, pain, and stress. Lemon Cherry Gelato features an aroma of lime, berries, and citrus with flavors of lemon, and sweet fruit. The dominant terpene of this strain is caryophyllene.

data.name: Living Soil Pre-rolls
data.desc: No Till Living Soil requires an immense amount of knowledge of soil  biology and microbiology. It is a very mathematical and precise way of growing when doing it commercially. Through extensive soil testing with  third party labs, No Till Kings is able to solve complex mathematical  equations to understand exactly what their soil needs cycle after cycle. They  have now used the same body of soil since they started their journey years ago and it keeps getting better!

products.name: Larry Strawberry
products.desc: Larry Strawberry is bred by Jungle Boys and is a cross of Mike Larry and Strawberry Shortcake. This cultivar is an indica dominant hybrid that has a euphoric yet calming high that's perfect for day and night. This cultivar displays aromas of strawberry shortbread cookies mixed with sweet cream. Beautifully tight sticky buds with both green and purple, make this strain shine!

products.name: Lazer Fuel
products.desc: Lazer Fuel is a cross between Gary Payton x Falcon-9 (Reverse). This heavy Indica dominant strain is mostly purple with slight hues of green and orange hairs. This strain has a powerful fuel aroma and tastes like licorice candy dipped in race gas. Trichomes cover this beautiful looking flower making it stand out amongst others. The high octane smelling flowers boasts a heavy full body experience that is perfect for sleeping or relaxing with some friends after a long day.

products.name: Neon Sunshine
products.desc: This heavy leaning indica strain is crossed between a Zkittlez mother and Falcon-9 (Reverse). Bred by Exotic Genetix, this flower has intense orange citrus aromas mixed with a light octane fuel. Neon Sunshine has beautiful inner purple calyxes and green hues. While exhaling the smoke, you will notice a gassy orange citrus mixture that tantalizes your taste buds. A good relaxing full bodied high accompanied with heavy eyes and an increased appetite is what some may feel when enjoying this amazing flower.

data.name: Nug THCa Diamond Pre-Roll
data.desc:
Nug THCa Diamond Pre-Roll
- THCa

THCA DIAMOND INFUSED
2019 FIRST PLACE WINNER
CANNABIS CUP BEST PRE-ROLL
What makes this award-winning product special is a combination of advanced techniques and a simple dedication to outstanding quality. The base of each joint is just under a gram of bud from our expertly-cultivated indoor gardens. This delivers an intoxicating compliment of terpenes and the unique entourage effects of the consumer’s chosen strain.
To this, we add pulverized THCa diamonds. Grown in our lab, these represent the purest form of this sought-after cannabinoid available to the market. Finishing the gram with this special ingredient kicks each pre- rolls potency into overdrive. While the terpenes modulate the character of the experience, this extra punch THC keeps the intensity at maximum.
