data.name: Premium Flower Slims 20PK
data.desc:
Slim pre-rolls are the perfect choice for those on the move. From hanging with friends to taking in a concert, slim pre-rolls help you elevate any experience.

Premium Flower
Some pre-rolls use shake or trim, which give you a lower-quality smoke. But that’s not what you’ll get from Pacific Stone Slims.
We utilize premium, 100% California greenhouse flower in every single Slims pre-roll. By using only higher-quality flower, we produce a more flavorful, smoother smoke.

Carefully Packed
Each Slims pre-roll is packed to our highest standards. We thoroughly pack and weigh every single pre-roll to ensure a consistent experience for you. Our .35g pack size is perfect for a single-use smoking experience.

Open again and again
The custom Slims pre-roll tin has a smooth, spring-loaded, double-sided button.

A smooth Smoke
With an eco-friendly hemp paper filter tip and less paper, our Slims produce a cooler burn, meaning a smoother smoke. With less paper, you’ll get more green in every puff.

products.desc:
20-pack Premium Greenhouse Flower 7.0g

805 Glue is a cannabis strain believed to have originated in the Central Coast region of California. The exact lineage of 805 Glue is not clear, but it is believed to be a hybrid of two or more strains, including the famous Gorilla Glue #4 (Sour Dub x Chocolate Diesel) and Chems Sister, a not-so-known strain from the local area.
The strain is highly regarded for its balanced effects, which can induce a powerful yet relaxing high suitable for daytime and nighttime use. When consumed, 805 Glue can help to boost mood, creativity, and energy levels while also providing a calming and relaxing sensation throughout the body.

data.name: Premium Pre-Roll
data.desc:
Overview
Aside from CBX's legendary cultivation techniques, they have a multitude of unique quality control practices we follow after we cut down our plants that ensure the passion they put into our products is apparent to every customer who enjoys them. Once CBX harvests a strains, they are working to guarantee maximum trichome preservation. All Cannabiotix flower is dried in complete darkness, using the traditional hang-dry method, and their dry rooms are religiously monitored to ensure ideal conditions throughout the drying and curing process. Once dry, none of their buds are groped during the trimming process, as hand trimmers use our unique “revolve the stem” technique, to ensure our flowers retain the maximum amount of trichomes through the manicuring process. These are critical elements to one of the quality points CBX hangs their hats on, which is delivering glistening, crystal covered, resin rich, gem like diamond buds in every single CBX jar we sell.

100% premium flower, no trim, all natural paper.

Volume
.75 gram Cannabiotix pre-roll.

products.name: Apples & Diamonds
products.desc: Apples and Diamonds is a delectable Hybrid that combines the finest traits from two time-honored strains. With an alluring aroma of diesel and musk and a bud structure that reflects its Black Diamond X lineage, these distinct calyxes showcase an elevated Golden Applez flavor. Each seasoned breath emits piquant notes of cracked black peppercorn and lemon rind, offering hints of dried apple and floral accents that culminate into a smooth, flawless smoke.

products.name: Sour Sangria
products.desc: Sour Sangria is an award-winning Sativa with a sophisticated flavor profile and well-balanced high. This compelling cross of our own Yuzu Mac and Pandora makes for dense, resinous nugs that display vivid blue and Fuschia tones. Its sweet, sour, and citrus-forward nose translates to a refreshing inhale, while floral, earthy, and peppery notes make for a bold exhalation. While this high can have calming and reflective qualities, its uplifting nature keeps the mind sharp, focused, and engaged.

products.name: Widows Glaze
products.desc: Widows Glaze, the heaviest of all the Indicas, is a potent cross between our fabled Medusa and GMO. Wiry orange hairs contrast the airy purple buds that are clouded in thick layers of glossy trichomes. With an aroma just as pungent, eye-squinting notes of pine and sweet diesel accentuate each garlic spiced inhale, while undertones of fresh lavender come forward on the exhale. While GMO aids in elevating the mind, this strain preserves the ultimate traits from its Medusa lineage, with a body high so powerful that one fatal hit can turn you to stone.

products.desc: Experience a galaxy of flavor with Violet Dreamsicle—this strain boasts dark purple hues and frosty, candy-like crystals that create a space-like visual experience. As an indica, it gently guides you into a dreamlike state, where sweet tastes and frost-covered nugs leave you questioning whether your experience is too good to be true. products.name: Blue Agapē
products.desc: Blue Agapē, an Indica cross of our Blue Lotus and White Runtz and the first strain we released through our Research & Development line, is a potent, hard-hitting strain with a memorable Terpene profile. Because of its high Terpene content, this Indica offers a bold aroma, flavor profile, and unique and long-lasting high. Earthy, spicy, pine-forward notes experienced upon breaking the nugs apart are enhanced with every flavor-packed hit. Like its parent strains, Blue Agapē offers a mellow, relaxing high.

products.name: Golden Applez
products.desc: Golden Applez, a cross of our Golden Hour and Fried Applez, is a dreamy, flavorful Hybrid with a strong head high and a soothing sense of full-body relaxation. Its dense nugs have a structure similar to its parent strain, Fried Applez, and a color palette reminiscent of Golden Hour - with wiry, amber Stigmas laid between clusters of frosty Trichomes. Fresh, fruity notes of apple and lemon are at the forefront of this strain's aroma, with a subtle hint of spice and hops on the finish. Its flavor profile follows suit, with a sweet, fruity inhale and an earthy, herbal exhale that induces a mellow, calming buzz. While the body melts into a relaxed state, the mind drifts off into euphoria, making this balanced Hybrid an excellent choice for any time of day.

products.name: 30mg
products.desc:
1 Fl Oz
It works instantly! We use a patent-pending process for our cannabinoids, so the particles absorb within seconds. Gone are the days of needing to wait one our for a cannabis lube to wait for 60 minutes for your lube to activate. Kush Queen is a female-owned brand, so we took the development of this product very seriously. We were horrified to discover most cannabis lubes were coconut oil based. Coconut oil is NOT and has never been acceptable as a personal lubricant. It alters the body's pH and will promote the growth of yeast and is NOT latex compatible. Kush Queen Ignite is paraben free, petrochemical free, latex compatible, and non-staining.
